20share%20price%20manipulation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20Ahli%20used%20Gulf%20Asia%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20Limited%2C%20Chang%20used%20Lingo%20Investment%20Limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20stated.%20Emerging%20India%20Focus%20Funds%20(Mauritius)%20and%20the%20EM%20Resurgent%20Fund%20(Mauritius)%20under%20the%20Global%20Opportunities%20Fund%20(Bermuda)%20channelled%20funds%20through%20these%20two%20BVI%20shell%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20Adani%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20the%20Black%20Money%20Was%20Brought%20Back%20to%20India%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fhow-the-black-money-was-brought-back-to-india%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Black%20Money%20Was%20Brought%20Back%20to%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCorporate%20records%2C%20accessed%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20reveal%20the%20web%20of%20networks%20through%20which%20office-bearers%20and%20employees%20of%20Adani%20companies%20controlled%20these%20two%20BVI%20shell%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20month%20after%20Gulf%20Asia%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20Limited%20(BVI)%20was%20incorporated%20in%20May%202011%2C%20records%20show%2C%20a%20Dubai-based%20Chartered%20Accountant%20firm%20wrote%20to%20Trident%20Trust%20asking%20whether%20%E2%80%9Chand%20written%20documents%20will%20be%20accepted%E2%80%A6%20when%20they%20want%20to%20do%20the%20share%20transfer%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20share%20transfer%20agreement%20said%20Ahli%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdesirous%20of%20selling%20his%20100%25%20shareholding%E2%80%9D%20to%20one%20Rakesh%20Shantilal%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRakesh%20Shantilal%20Shah%20in%201996%20replaced%20Vinod%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Ranjanben%20as%20director%20in%20GA%20Internatio