ent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20shared%20by%20Anton%20Gerashchenko%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20advisor%20to%20the%20Minister%20of%20Internal%20Affairs%20of%20Ukraine.%20He%20asks%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20going%20on%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAn%20interesting%20post%20on%20the%20Telegram%20channel%20of%20%26quot%3BZ-blogger%26quot%3B%20Pozdnyakov%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BGod%2C%20don't%20you%20leave%20us%20%F0%9F%99%8F%F0%9F%99%8F%F0%9F%99%8F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPray%20to%20God%20you%20are%20alive%20and%20healthy%20%F0%9F%99%8F%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhat%20is%20going%20on%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fw1mlbuQyfx%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fw1mlbuQyfx%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Anton%20Gerashchenko%20(%40Gerashchenko_en)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGerashchenko_en%2Fstatus%2F1696071567292117414%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20posts%20has%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20comments%20from%20users%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProbably%20nothing%2C%20but%20if%20he's%20sick%20and%20his%20time%20is%20nearing%20the%20end%2C%20then%20it%20actually%20makes%20perfect%20sense%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20Prigozjin.%20He%20would%20most%20certainly%20try%20to%20take%20over%20if%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20one%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20only%20pray%20this%20is%20the%20case!%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20the%20Russian%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvladimir-putin-suffers-from-blurred-vision-and-numb-tongue-doctors-panic-over-his-health-report-3938607%5C%22%3Eis%20suffering%20from%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20pain%20in%20his%20head%2C%20blurred%20vision%2C%20and%20numbness%20of%20the%20tongue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20claims%20were%20made%20by%20the%20General%20SVR%20Telegram%20channel%2C%20a%20Russian%20outlet%20that%20has%20been%20making%20claims%20about%20Mr%20Putin's%20ailing%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693546320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F8nie6n7g_vladimir-putin-ukraine-afp_625x300_18_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhats-going-on-ukraine-officials-post-on-putins-health-goes-viral-4347363%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rumours%20about%20Vadimir%20Putin's%20health%20have%20increased%20since%20Russia%20launched%20an%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhats-going-on-ukraine-officials-post-on-putins-health-goes-viral-4347363%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhats-going-on-ukraine-officials-post-on-putins-health-goes-viral-4347363%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhats-going-on-ukraine-officials-post-on-putins-health-goes-viral-4347363%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Forms%20Panel%20On%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%2C%20Ex%20President%20To%20Head%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20on%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20proposal%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20study%20the%20issue%20and%20submit%20a%20report.%20The%20panel%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Centre%20had%20announced%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%20from%20September%2018%20to%2022.%20Ever%20since%20the%20surprise%20announcement%20was%20made%2C%20there%20has%20been%20speculation%20that%20a%20bill%20on%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20will%20be%20tabled%20during%20the%20session%2C%20but%20no%20one%20from%20the%20government%20has%20confirmed%20this%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'One%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20refers%20to%20holding%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assembly%20polls%20simultaneously%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20have%20spoken%20on%20the%20issue%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20and%20it%20was%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20for%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConducting%20polls%20simultaneously%20was%20the%20norm%20in%20India%20until%201967%20and%20four%20elections%20were%20held%20this%20way.%20The%20practice%20stopped%20after%20some%20state%20assemblies%20were%20dissolved%20prematurely%20in%201968-69.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20also%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20dissolved%20a%20year%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20in%201970%20and%20mid-term%20elections%20had%20been%20held%20in%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20Manifesto%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20promised%20to%20evolve%20a%20method%20for%20holding%20the%C2%A0%20Assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPage%2014%20of%20the%20manifesto%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20committed%20to%20initiate%20electoral%20reforms%20to%20eliminate%20criminals.%20The%20BJP%20will%20seek%2C%20through%20consultation%20with%20other%20parties%2C%20to%20evolve%20a%20method%20of%20holding%20Assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20simultaneously.%20Apart%20from%20reducing%20election%20expenses%20for%20both%20political%20parties%20and%20Government%2C%20this%20will%20ensure%20certain%20stability%20for%20State%20Governments.%20We%20will%20also%20look%20at%20revising%20expenditure%20limits%20realistically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20spoken%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%202016%20and%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202019%2C%20he%20had%20called%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue.%20The%20meeting%20had%20been%20skipped%20by%20several%20opposition%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20argued%20that%20holding%20elections%20every%20few%20months%20puts%20a%20burden%20on%20the%20nation's%20resources%20and%20causes%20a%20break%20in%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20first%20political%20reactions%20to%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20General%20Secretary%20D%20Raja%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20obsessed%20with%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20party%20and%20it%20has%20been%20jittery%20since%20the%20opposition%20united%20under%20the%20INDIA%20banner.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20nation%2C%20one%20election%20is%20not%20a%20new%20issue.%20It%20has%20been%20discussed%20for%20several%20years.%20Ever%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%2C%20it%20has%20been%20obsessed%20with%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20culture%3B%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20religion%3B%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20language%3B%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20tax%3B%20now%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%3B%20then%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20party%3B%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20leader.%20That%20is%20the%20obsession%20the%20BJP%20is%20suffering%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raja%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDr%20Ambedkar%20said%20Parliament%20is%20supreme%20in%20our%20democracy%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20is%20undermining%20Parliament.%20Increasingly%2C%20our%20Parliament%20is%20becoming%20redundant.%20But%20they%20called%20a%20special%20session.%20Nobody%20knows%20what%20the%20purpose%20is.%20Ever%20since%20the%20opposition%20parties%20came%20together%20under%20the%20INDIA%20banner%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20jittery%20and%20desperate.%20Mr%20Modi%20is%20jittery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20said%20making%20the%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20proposal%20a%20reality%20will%20require%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20and%20the%20support%20of%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20members%20in%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20polls%20in%20five%20states%20-%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram%20-%20are%20due%20in%20November-December%2C%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20around%20May%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693546200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2Fqeklno2_voting-generic-up-pti-650_650x400_07_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-move-on-one-nation-one-election-panel-formed-to-explore-possibility-4347165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20on%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20proposal%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20study%20the%20issue%20and%20submit%20a%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-move-on-one-nation-one-election-panel-formed-to-explore-possibility-4347165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-move-on-one-nation-one-election-panel-formed-to-explore-possibility-4347165%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-move-on-one-nation-one-election-panel-formed-to-explore-possibility-4347165%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Decoding%20Meri%20Pyaari%20Bindu's%20ending%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693546200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103248562%2Cimgsize-47730.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2F