onal%20assessing%20officer%20undertook%20the%20exercise%20of%20reassessment%20of%20his%20income%20for%20the%20impugned%20financial%20years%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-issues-show-cause-notice-to-chandrababu-naidu-for-alleged-kickbacks-worth-118-crore-101693507669903.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20case%20is%20notified%20to%20this%20office%20(Central%20Circle)%2C%20immediately%20to%20commence%20the%20proceedings%2C%20notice%20under%20section%20153C%20was%20validly%20issued%20and%20the%20proceedings%20are%20in%20progress%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20the%20show-cause%20notice%2C%20adding%20the%20department%20has%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20unaccounted%20income%20generated%20through%20bogus%20sub-contracts%20was%20given%20to%20Naidu%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20153C%20of%20the%20I-T%20Act%20allows%20the%20revenue%20department%20to%20proceed%20against%20a%20party%20other%20than%20the%20person%20who%20has%20been%20searched%2C%20if%20certain%20incriminating%20materials%20are%20found%20against%20that%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigations%20against%20Naidu%20began%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-issues-show-cause-notice-to-chandrababu-naidu-for-alleged-kickbacks-worth-118-crore-101693507669903.html%5C%22%3Esearches%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20one%20Manoj%20Vasudev%20Pardasany%3C%2Fa%3E%20(referred%20to%20as%20MVP%20in%20the%20notice)%20who%20was%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20tendering%20process%20in%20the%20state%20since%20December%202017%20on%20behalf%20of%20Shapoorji%20Pallonji%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(SPCL)%2C%20and%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20Pardasany%E2%80%99s%20associates%20in%20November%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statements%2C%20Pardasany%20admitted%20to%20havin