party.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20other%20agenda%20at%20the%20crucial%20meeting%20include%20choosing%20a%20logo%20for%20the%20alliance%20and%20appointment%20of%20spokesperson.%20The%20alliance%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20hold%20discussions%20on%20whether%20to%20have%20a%20convenor%20or%20not.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBesides%20the%20coordination%20committee%2C%20there%20will%20be%20four%20sub-groups%20to%20plan%20the%20campaign%C2%A0and%20rallies%2C%C2%A0handle%20social%20media%20and%20manage%20the%20data%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20told%20the%20leaders%20that%20the%20bloc%20should%20release%20its%20manifesto%20by%20October%202%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20asked%20them%20to%20prepare%20a%20common%20agenda%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%20on%20national%20level.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELast%20night%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20hosted%20a%20formal%20dinner%20for%20the%20Opposition%20leaders.%20At%20the%20meeting%2C%20several%20leaders%20expressed%20apprehension%20about%20early%20polls.%C2%A0Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20should%20be%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20the%20NDA's%20%26quot%3Bsurprise%20element%20strategy%20and%20gimmicks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20has%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20session%20of%20Parliament%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20held%20from%20September%2018%20to%2022%2C%20drawing%20strong%20criticism%C2%A0from%20the%20Opposition.%20Government%20sources%20have%2C%20so%20far%2C%20been%20tight-lipped%20on%20possible%20agendas.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20leaders%20said%20they%20have%20come%20together%20to%20save%20the%20Constitution%20and%20democracy%20and%20that%20the%20alliance%20is%20working%20to%20unite%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20just%20a%20coalition%20of%20parties%20but%20that%20of%20ideas%2C%20%26quot%3B%20said%20RJD%20leader%20Manoj%20Jha.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20grouping%20was%20held%20in%20Patna%20on%20June%2023%20and%20the%20second%20meeting%20was%20convened%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20July.%20The%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20unity%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20country%2C%20said%20Former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Lalu%20Prasad.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20termed%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20a%20%26quot%3Bselfish%20alliance%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20and%20protecting%20the%20interests%20of%20families%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20its%20member%20parties.%C2%A0Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20claimed%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20members%20have%20come%20together%20to%20save%20their%20own%20political%20interests.%20%26quot%3BINDIA%20alliance%20is%20agenda-less.%20Their%20only%20agenda%20is%20to%20remove%20PM%20Modi%20from%20his%20post.%20Once%20PM%20Modi%20finds%20a%20place%20in%20people's%20minds%2C%20not%2036%20but%20even%20if%20100%20parties%20come%20together%2C%20they%20cannot%20remove%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693542960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4iq4e9v8_india-bloc_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-alliance-india-bloc-mumbai-opposition-meeting-bjp-congress-key-decisions-likely-at-india-blocs-3rd-meet-at-mumbai-today-10-facts-4347065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20third%20formal%20meeting%20of%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20will%20be%20held%20today%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20about%2063%20representatives%20from%2028%20opposition%20parties%20will%20take%20key%20decisions%20and%20finalise%20the%20action%20plan%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-alliance-india-bloc-mumbai-opposition-meeting-bjp-congr