t%20during%20the%20showpiece%20event%20due%20to%20a%20groin%20strain%20he%20had%20sustained%20while%20training%20in%20May-June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20began%20with%20a%20modest%2080.79m%20which%20put%20him%20in%20the%20second%20spot%20but%20he%20fouled%20the%20next%20two%20throws%20to%20slip%20to%20fifth%20at%20the%20halfway%20stage%20when%20Germany's%20Julian%20Weber%20was%20leading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Chopra%20pulled%20off%2085.22m%20in%20his%20fourth%20attempt%20which%20saw%20him%20rise%20to%20second.%20By%20that%20time%2C%20Vadlejch%20had%20taken%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20fouled%20his%20fifth%20throw%20again%20bit%20achieved%20his%20best%20of%20the%20day%20--%2085.71m%20--%20in%20his%20last%20throw.%20%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20video%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Em%20-%20Another%20Neeraj%20Chopra%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Men's%20Javelin%20Throw%20World%20Champion%20sealed%20qualification%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDiamondLeague%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DiamondLeague%3C%2Fa%3E%20final%20in%20Eugene%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnKeep%20watching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWandaDiamondLeague%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WandaDiamondLeague%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FJioCinema%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23JioCinema%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26amp%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSports18%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Sports18%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FElvishYadav%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ElvishYadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fneerajchopra%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23neerajch