as%20launched%20following%20the%20communal%20polarisation%20triggered%20by%20the%202013%20riots%20%E2%80%93%20attended%20the%20rituals%20in%20Kawal%20this%20year%2C%20too.%20A%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20he%20holds%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20fisheries%2C%20animal%20husbandry%20and%20dairying%20portfolio%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20attending%20the%20%3Cem%3Epuja-havan%3C%2Fem%3E%20ceremony%20held%20in%20Kawal%20in%20memory%20of%20the%20two%20Hindu%20youths%20%E2%80%93%20Gaurav%20and%20Sachin%20%E2%80%93%20Balyan%2C%20who%20was%20among%20those%20booked%20for%20inciting%20the%20communal%20violence%20in%202013%2C%20tweeted%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6prayed%20for%20the%20peace%20of%20both%20the%20departed%20souls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Jat%20by%20caste%2C%20the%20minister%20belongs%20to%20the%20Kutbi%20village%2C%20which%20along%20with%20its%20connected%20settlement%20Kutba%2C%20was%20among%20the%20worst-affected%20during%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaurav%20and%20Sachin%E2%80%99s%20deaths%20are%20often%20evoked%20by%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20including%20by%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%20political%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots%20of%202013%20led%20to%20unprecedented%20communal%20polarisation%20in%20western%20UP%2C%20breaking%20old%20electoral%20and%20social%20bonds%20between%20Muslims%20and%20Jats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Harmony%20Lost%20Out%3A%20Voices%20from%20Western%20UP%20Over%20the%20Years%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwestern-up-jats-elections-2019%5C%22%3EHow%20Harmony%20Lost%20Out%3A%20Voices%20from%20Western%20UP%20Over%20the%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20from%20which%20several%20leaders%20and%20legislators%20were%20accused%20of%20instigating%20the%20riots%2C%20reaped%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20communal%20divide%20in%20the%20state%2C%20especially%20in%20western%20UP.%20This%20is%20a%20phenomenon%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20find%20a%20formidable%20counter%20to%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20on%2C%20the%20fight%20for%20justice%20has%20moved%20at%20a%20snail%E2%80%99s%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20information%20gathered%20through%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%20Shamli-based%20activist%20Akram%20Choudhary%20found%20out%20in%20October%202019%20that%20the%20police%20had%20lodged%20510%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20in%20the%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%2C%20the%20additional%20SP%20of%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20special%20investigation%20team%20who%20probed%20the%20cases%20informed%20Choudhary%20that%20final%20reports%20had%20been%20submitted%20in%20165%20cases%2C%20including%2019%20murder%20cases.%20There%20were%2047%20cases%20in%20which%20the%20offence%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20was%20lodged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%2014%20of%20these%20were%20dismissed%20during%20investigation%2C%20and%20the%20final%20report%20was%20submitted%20for%20want%20of%20evidence%20in%2015%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChargesheets%20were%20filed%20in%2018%20FIRs.%20The%20police%20found%20170%20FIRs%20to%20be%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F23163245%2Fmuzaffarnagar-train-station.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F23163245%2Fmuzaffarnagar-train-station.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F23163245%2Fmuzaffarnagar-train-station-300x158.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F23163245%2Fmuzaffarnagar-train-station-768x403.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F23163245%2Fmuzaffarnagar-train-station-1024x538.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-242297%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECredit%3A%20Superfast1111%20%2F%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202021%2C%20eight%20years%20since%20the%20communal%20violence%2C%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%20that%201%2C117%20persons%20accused%20in%2097%20cases%20related%20to%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20robbery%20and%20arson%20had%20been%20acquitted%20over%20time%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence.%20The%20UP%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20had%20decided%20to%20withdraw%2077%20cases%20related%20to%20the%20riots%20but%20the%20court%20had%20granted%20it%20permission%20for%20withdrawal%20in%20just%20one%20FIR%20which%20involved%20former%20BJP%20MLAs%20Sangeet%20Som%20and%20Suresh%20Rana%2C%20former%20BJP%20MP%20Bhartendu%20Singh%20and%20Hindu%20extremist%20leader%20Sadhvi%20Prachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvictions%20in%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20communal%20violence%20have%20been%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20In%20February%202019%2C%20a%20trial%20court%20convicted%20seven%20Muslims%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Gaurav%20and%20Sachin.%20Additional%20district%20and%20sessions%20judge%20Himanshu%20Bhatnagar%20sentenced%20the%20seven%20%E2%80%93%20Muzammil%2C%20Furqan%2C%20Jahangir%2C%20Nadeem%2C%20Afzaal%2C%20Iqbal%20and%20Muzassim%20%E2%80%93%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%20What%20actually%20happened%20on%20August%2027%20and%2028%2C%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20deadly%20violence%20a%20week%20later%2C%20is%20still%20disputed%2C%20with%20contradictory%20narratives%20from%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicted%20men%20were%20related%20to%20Shahnawaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20at%20Jansath%20police%20station%20by%20Gaurav%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20Gaurav%2C%20a%20class%2012%20student%2C%20had%20a%20verbal%20spat%20with%20Muzassim%2C%20a%20relative%20of%20Shahnawaz%E2%80%99s%2C%20a%20day%20prior%20to%20the%20double%20murder%20after%20the%20Jat%20boy%E2%80%99s%20cycle%20collided%20with%20Muzassim%E2%80%99s%20motorcycle.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20when%20Gaurav%20was%20passing%20through%20Kawal%20along%20with%20his%20cousin%20Sachin%2C%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20Muzzasim%20and%20a%20group%20of%20other%20boys%20armed%20with%20sticks%20and%20a%20knife.%20Gaurav%20and%20Sachin%20died%20due%20to%20the%20assault.%20In%20their%20bail%20applications%20in%20the%20lower%20court%2C%20those%20accused%20of%20murdering%20Shahnawaz%20claimed%20that%20while%20he%20was%20among%20those%20assaulting%20Gaurav%20and%20Sachin%2C%20and%20he%20died%20of%20injuries%20suffered%20in%20self-defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mohammad%20Saleem%2C%20Shahnawaz%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20accused%20the%20Jat%20boys%20of%20beating%20up%20his%20son%20first%20and%20killing%20him%20over%20the%20collision%20of%20motorbikes.%20After%20the%20verbal%20spat%2C%20Gaurav%20allegedly%20gathered%20seven%20others%20and%20armed%20with%20swords%20and%20knives%20dragged%20Shahnawaz%20out%20of%20his%20house%20and%20assaulted%20him%20and%20others.%20Shahnawaz%20later%20died%20in%20hospital.%20The%20popular%20theory%20is%20that%20Gaurav%20and%20Sachin%20were%20killed%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Shahnawaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20undeniable%20is%20that%20the%20deaths%20of%20the%20three%20young%20men%20turned%20Muzaffarnagar%20into%20a%20cauldron%20of%20communal%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20single-member%20Vishnu%20Sahai%20commission%20that%20probed%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20communal%20violence%2C%20while%20absolving%20the%20then%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20of%20direct%20responsibility%20for%20the%20riots%2C%20blamed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cacute%20communal%20divide%E2%80%9D%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20and%20Shamli%20created%20by%20the%20Kawal%20murders.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20riots%20resulted%20out%20of%20the%20polarisation%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20Kawal%20incident%2C%20when%20one%20Muslim%20youth%20Shahnawaz%20and%20two%20Hindu%20youth%20Sachin%20and%20Gaurav%20were%20killed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Justice%20Sahai%20Commission%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20775-page%20report%2C%20which%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20UP%20assembly%20in%202016%2C%20mainly%20blamed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnegligence%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20local%20administration%20and%20%E2%80%9Cfailure%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20along%20with%20exaggerated%20reporting%20in%20social%20and%20print%20media%20for%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelving%20into%20the%20Kawal%20incident%2C%20Justice%20Sahai%20noted%20that%20the%20transfer%20of%20then%20district%20magistrate%20Surendra%20Singh%20and%20SSP%20Manzil%20Saini%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2027%20and%20the%20setting%20free%20of%20eight%20Muslim%20men%20by%20police%2C%20as%20they%20were%20not%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20or%20suspected%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20angered%20the%20local%20Hindus%2C%20especially%20the%20Jats.%20They%20felt%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20was%20working%20in%20favour%20of%20Muslims%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%20The%20situation%20got%20worse%20after%20the%20names%20of%20relatives%20of%20Gaurav%20and%20Sachin%20were%20added%20in%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Shahnawaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Five%20Years%20On%2C%20the%20Continuing%20Tragedy%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%20Is%20Our%20Collective%20Failure%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmuzaffarnagar-five-years-rape-victims-justice%5C%22%3EThe%20Continuing%20Tragedy%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%20Is%20Our%20Collective%20Failure%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Justice%20Sahai%20mentioned%20that%20inflammatory%20speeches%20were%20made%20by%20members%20of%20both%20communities%2C%20he%20also%20noted%20that%20due%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%20the%20administration%20was%20ill-equipped%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20panchayat%20of%20Nagla%20Mandaur%20called%20by%20Hindu%20groups%20on%20September%207%2C%202013%2C%20which%20led%20to%20large-scale%20violence.%20While%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%20had%20estimated%20a%20crowd%20of%2015%2C000-20%2C000%2C%20around%2040%2C000-50%2C000%20people%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20panchayat%2C%20noted%20Sahai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcourt-convicts-two-in-muzaffarnagar-riots-gang-rape-case%5C%22%3Econvicted%20two%20Hindu%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20gang%20raping%20a%20Muslim%20woman%20during%20the%20September%202013%20communal%20violence.%20The%20woman%2C%20whose%20house%20was%20looted%20and%20burnt%20on%20September%208%20that%20year%2C%20was%20raped%20by%20three%20men%20identified%20as%20Kuldeep%2C%20Sikander%20and%20Maheshveer%2C%20the%20court%20ruled.%20Kuldeep%20died%20during%20the%20trial.%20The%20court%20convicted%20the%20two%20men%20under%20376-D%20(gangrape)%2C%20376(2)(g)%20(rape%20during%20communal%20violence)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20Sikander%20and%20Maheshveer%20were%20handed%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20of%2020%20years%20with%20concurrent%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20victims%20continue%20their%20long%20legal%20battles%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20violence%20on%20the%20political%20landscape%20of%20the%20region%20can%20be%20felt%20even%20today.%20The%20BJP%20won%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20both%202014%20and%202019.%20In%20the%202017%20UP%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20all%20six%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20and%20two%20out%20of%20three%20in%20Shamli.%20However%2C%20in%20the%202022%20election%2C%20when%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20the%20alliance%20won%20all%20three%20seats%20in%20Shamli%20and%20four%20out%20of%20six%20in%20Muzaffarnagar.%20Among%20those%20scalped%20were%20Suresh%20Rana%20and%20Mriganka%20Singh%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20BJP%20leader%20Hukum%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20peddled%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhukum-singhs-defensiveness-on-the-kairana-exodus-exposes-the-bjps-hindutva-agenda%5C%22%3Efake%20theory%20of%20a%20Hindu%20exodus%20from%20Kairana%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016.%20Vikram%20Saini%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20BJP%20winners%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20was%20last%20year%20convicted%20in%20a%202013-related%20rioting%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693537770000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01083106%2FF4mmAjaXgAAeky-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ften-years-later-shadow-of-the-2013-riots-still-haunts-muzaffarnagar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20victims%20still%20wait%20for%20justice%2C%20a%20BJP%20minister%20visited%20Kawal%20village%20again%20this%20year%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20religious%20rituals%20on%20the%20death%20anniversary%20of%20two%20Hindu%20Jat%20youth%20whose%20killings%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Muslim%20young%20man%20%E2%80%93%20had%20triggered%20the%20riots.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ften-years-later-shadow-of-the-2013-riots-still-haunts-muzaffarnagar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%3A%20My%20assets%20are%20%E2%80%98Mona%20Lisas%E2%80%99%2C%20my%20name%20worth%20%243%20billion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A