al%20law%20and%20an%20international%20pact%20that%20recognise%20the%20shipwreck%20as%20a%20revered%20burial%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expedition%20is%20being%20organised%20by%20RMS%20Titanic%20Inc.%20(RMST)%2C%20a%20company%20based%20in%20Georgia%20that%20holds%20the%20salvage%20rights%20to%20the%20most%20well-known%20shipwreck%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20company%20showcases%20artefacts%20that%20have%20been%20retrieved%20from%20the%20location%20resting%20at%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20North%20Atlantic%2C%20encompassing%20items%20ranging%20from%20silverware%20to%20a%20segment%20of%20the%20Titanic's%20hull.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnecklace-made-from-megalodon-tooth-found-in-titanic-wreckage-ai-to-help-find-owner-4074075%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Necklace%20Made%20From%20Megalodon%20Tooth%20Found%20In%20Titanic%20Wreckage%2C%20AI%20To%20Help%20Find%20Its%20Owner%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F30%2Fscience%2Ftitanic-shipwreck-lawsuit.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20taking%20legal%20action%20to%20assert%20control%20over%20who%20can%20recover%20artefacts%20from%20the%20storied%20liner%20and%2C%20potentially%2C%20to%20block%20an%20expedition%20planned%20for%20next%20year.%20The%20move%20comes%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fwhat-caused-titanic-sub-implosion-708172%5C%22%3ETitan%20submersible%20disaster%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20June%2018%20raised%20questions%20about%20who%20controls%20access%20to%20the%20ship's%20remains%2C%20which%20lie%20more%20than%20two%20miles%20down%20on%20the%20North%20Atlantic%20seabed.%20The%20legal%20action%20is%20also%20notable%20because%20it%20pits%20the%20legislative%20and%20executive%20branches%20of%20government%20against%20the%20judicial%20branch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftitanic-survivors-letter-describing-near-miss-before-it-hit-iceberg-auctioned-4139669%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Titanic%20Survivor's%20Letter%20Describing%20Near-Miss%20Before%20It%20Hit%20Iceberg%20Auctioned%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20is%20now%20seeking%20to%20become%20a%20party%20to%20the%20salvage%20case%20and%20block%20any%20expedition%20it%20deems%20objectionable.%20It%20claims%20the%20legal%20right%20to%20have%20the%20Secretary%20of%20Commerce%20and%20its%20maritime%20unit%2C%20the%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%2C%20or%20NOAA%2C%20approve%20or%20deny%20permission%20to%20RMS%20Titanic%20whenever%20%26quot%3Bthe%20company%26quot%3B%20seeks%20the%20court's%20permission%20to%20conduct%20more%20artefact%20recoveries%2C%20reported%20the%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20a%20long%20time%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20Ole%20Varmer%2C%20a%20retired%20lawyer%20for%20NOAA%20who%20specialises%20in%20shipwreck%20conservation%2C%20told%20the%20NYT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20forced%20to%20intervene%20as%20a%20party%20and%20ask%20the%20court%20to%20enforce%20these%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201912%2C%20during%20its%20inaugural%20journey%20from%20Southampton%20to%20New%20York%2C%20the%20ship%20collided%20with%20an%20iceberg%20and%20subsequently%20sank%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20over%201%2C500%20lives%20among%20the%202%2C208%20passengers%20and%20crew%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20concerns%20of%20the%20US%20government%20is%20the%20potential%20disruption%20of%20any%20human%20remains%20that%20could%20still%20be%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693537260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fvb5jrajo_titanic-_625x300_21_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt