tted%20line%20on%20the%20map%20are%20%26quot%3Binvalid%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20statement%2C%20which%20cited%20Pham%20Thu%20Hang%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20Vietnam's%20foreign%20affairs%20ministry.%20Vietnam%20%26quot%3Bresolutely%20opposes%20all%20China's%20claims%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20based%20on%20the%20dotted%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Hang%20added%20in%20the%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20countries%20have%20also%20rejected%20the%20map.%20India%20on%20Tuesday%20took%20issue%20with%20a%20part%20of%20the%20map%20that%20shows%20sections%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20under%20China's%20control.%20And%20the%20Philippines%20said%20it%20doesn't%20recognize%20China's%20expansive%20claims%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%20Governments%20of%20Malaysia%20and%20Taiwan%20have%20also%20issued%20strongly%20worded%20statements%20accusing%20Beijing%20of%20claiming%20their%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20map%20at%20a%20regular%20press%20briefing%20Wednesday%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesman%20Wang%20Wenbin%20said%20his%20government%20hoped%20the%20%26quot%3Brelevant%20sides%20can%20remain%20objective%20and%20calm%20and%20refrain%20from%20overinterpreting.%26quot%3B%20China%20released%20the%20map%20so%20publishers%2C%20companies%20and%20others%20have%20an%20official%20version%20to%20reference.%20Foreign%20firms%20sometimes%20run%20into%20trouble%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%20over%20how%20they%20use%20maps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20claims%20more%20than%2080%25%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20and%20backs%20up%20its%20claim%20with%20a%201947%20map%20that%20shows%20vague%20dashes%20-%20the%20nine-dash%20line%20--%20looping%20down%20to%20a%20point%20about%201%2C100%20miles%20(1%2C800%20kilometers)%20south%20of%20Hainan%20Island.%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Brunei%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Taiwan%20claim%20parts%20of%20the%20same%20maritime%20area%2C%20and%20have%20sparred%20with%20China%20over%20where%20the%20boundaries%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693536300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fsouth-china-sea_625x300_1527129222399.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-india-philippines-malaysia-vietnam-and-taiwan-also-reject-new-china-map-4347062%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vietnam%20said%20China's%20official%20map%20released%20this%20week%20violates%20its%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20Spratly%20and%20Paracel%20Islands%20and%20jurisdiction%20over%20its%20waters%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20the%20nation's%20government%20news%20website.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-india-philippines-malaysia-vietnam-and-taiwan-also-reject-new-china-map-4347062%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-india-philippines-malaysia-vietnam-and-taiwan-also-reject-new-china-map-4347062%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-india-philippines-malaysia-vietnam-and-taiwan-also-reject-new-china-map-4347062%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Howdy%20Doody'%3A%20Police%20stop%20Nebraska%20man%20for%20driving%20with%20huge%20bull%20in%20passenger%20seat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693536118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103262651%2Cimgsize-960351.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhowdy-doody-police-stop-nebraska-man-for-driving-with-huge-bull-in-passenger-seat%2Farticleshow%2F103262667.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src