ace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fkushi-movie-review-and-release-live-updates-vijay-deverakonda-and-samantha-ruth-prabhus-film-now-playing-in-theatres%2Fliveblog%2F103262677.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Past%20and%20Future%20of%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20%E2%80%93%20And%20Why%20Both%20are%20Attractive%20to%20the%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31161555%2FUntitled-design-8-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20premature%20release%20of%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20minister%20and%20strongman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20politician%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%2C%20who%20was%20convicted%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20poet%20Madhumita%20Shukla%2C%20has%20created%20a%20stir%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20Purvanchal%C2%A0%20especially%20in%20Gorakhpur-Basti%20division%20with%20speculations%20rife%20about%20his%20prospective%20comeback%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShukla%20was%20murdered%20on%20May%209%2C%202003%2C%20at%20her%20Paper%20Mill%20residence%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmarmani%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Madhumani%2C%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20the%20murder%2C%20along%20with%20two%20others.%20The%20political%20career%20of%20Amarmani%2C%20a%20four-time%20MLA%20from%20Laxmipur%20(now%20Nautanwa)%20assembly%20constituency%20of%20Maharajganj%20district%2C%20had%20halted%20after%20the%20sentence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20well%20known%20that%20he%20has%20maintained%20his%20political%20grip%20on%20Nautanwa%20as%20well%20as%20the%20parliamentary%20constituency%20of%20Maharajganj%20through%20his%20family.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20as%20well%20as%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20are%20keen%20to%20figure%20out%20his%20prospective%20political%20utility%20for%20the%20elections%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeginnings%20in%20caste%20conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmarmani%20is%20a%20product%20of%20the%20Thakur-Brahmin%20caste%20conflict%20that%20erupted%20in%20Gorakhpur%20in%20the%201980s.%20His%20uncle%2C%20the%20former%20minister%20Shyamnarayan%20Tiwari%20was%20at%20the%20time%20active%20in%20politics%20and%20had%20been%20elected%20MLA%20from%20Pharenda%20area%20of%20Maharajganj%20district%20in%201974.%20But%20Amarmani%20forayed%20into%20politics%20as%20a%20right-hand%20man%20of%20strongman%20leader%20Harishankar%20Tiwari.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Virendra%20Pratap%20Shahi%20was%20leading%20the%20Thakurs%20against%20Harishankar.%20After%20losing%20the%201974%20assembly%20elections%20from%20Basti%2C%20Virendra%20contested%20from%20Laxmipur%20assembly%20in%20Maharajganj%20in%201980.%20The%20seat%20was%20the%20stronghold%20of%20Congress%20and%20Lok%20Dal%20leaders%20and%20at%20the%20time%2C%20only%20once%2C%20in%201967%2C%20had%20anyone%20else%20won%20it.%20The%20exception%2C%20Raghuraj%20Singh%2C%20had%20got%20this%20seat%20on%20a%20Jan%20Sangh%20ticket.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarishankar%20and%20his%20camp%20pitted%20Amarmani%20against%20Virendra%20in%20Laxmipur%20for%20the%20assembly%20seat.%20Both%20Virendra%20and%20Amarmani%20contested%20as%20independents%20while%20Fateh%20Bahadur%20Singh%20was%20the%20candidate%20from%20Janata%20Party.%20He%20was%20a%20staunch%20socialist%20and%20had%20served%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20union%20of%20DAV%20Degree%20College%2C%20Gorakhpur.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20kidnapping%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Amarmani%20in%20his%20very%20first%20election.%20When%20Fateh%20Bahadur%20refused%20to%20back%20out%20from%20the%20election%20despite%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20threats%2C%20the%20latter%20tried%20to%20kidnap%20him%20too.%20Recalling%20the%20incident%2C%20Fateh%20Bahadur%20says%20that%20he%20was%20sitting%20at%20a%20shop%20in%20Nautanwa%20when%20several%20vehicles%20showed%20up%20with%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20men%20who%20tried%20to%20forcibly%20shove%20him%20into%20one%20of%20the%20vehicles.%20They%20told%20him%20that%20they%20would%20take%20him%20to%20Nepal%20and%20kill%20him.%20Fateh%20Bahadur%20got%20an%20FIR%20registered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20Amarmani%20lost%20the%20election%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20secure%2019%2C289%20votes.%20In%201985%2C%20he%20lost%20to%20Virendra%20again.%20He%20had%20contested%20both%20these%20elections%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20elections%20held%20in%201989%2C%20Amarmani%20finally%20became%20an%20MLA%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20winning%20on%20a%20tiny%20margin.%20He%20had%20contested%20this%20election%20as%20an%20independent%20as%20well.%20But%20the%20situation%20had%20completely%20changed.%20Virendra%20Pratap%20Shahi%2C%20who%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Janata%20Party%2C%20had%20joined%20the%20Sanjay%20Vichar%20Manch%20formed%20by%20Maneka%20Gandhi%20and%20conducted%20many%20public%20meetings%20for%20her%20in%20Maharajganj%20and%20Gorakhpur.%20Soon%20after%2C%20he%20joined%20V.P.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Morcha.%20Virendra%20participated%20in%20a%20major%20rally%20held%20by%20V.P.%20Singh%20at%20the%20Tamkuhi%20Kothi%20grounds%20in%20Gorakhpur.%20Pipraich%20MLA%20Kedarnath%20Singh%20was%20the%20moderator%20on%20stage.%20When%20Virendra%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20deliver%20a%20speech%2C%20his%20supporters%20created%20a%20ruckus.%20Block%20chief%20Rampravesh%20Singh%2C%20one%20of%20Virendra%E2%80%99s%20supporters%2C%20even%20misbehaved%20with%20Kedarnath%20Singh.%20The%20incident%20miffed%20V.P.%20Singh%20and%20in%20turn%20damaged%20Virendra%E2%80%99s%20political%20career.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVirendra%2C%20who%20was%20eyeing%20a%20Janata%20Dal%20ticket%20from%20Maharajganj%20in%20the%201989%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20was%20not%20given%20a%20ticket%20owing%20to%20the%20incident.%20The%20ticket%20was%20instead%20given%20to%20Harshvardhan%2C%20a%20Janata%20Party%20MLA%20from%20Pharenda.%20The%20party%20asked%20Virendra%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20Laxmipur%20assembly%20seat%20but%20he%20refused.%20He%20simultaneously%20contested%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Maharajganj%20and%20the%20assembly%20election%20from%20Laxmipur.%20His%20close%20aide%20Akhilesh%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20keen%20to%20contest%20from%20Laxmipur%2C%20rebelled%20and%20entered%20the%20fray%20from%20the%20seat%20as%20well.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20fight%20for%20the%20Laxmipur%20assembly%20seat%20turned%20into%20a%20triangular%20contest%20which%20gave%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20the%20edge%20and%20he%20defeated%20Akhilesh%20Singh%20in%20the%20last%20round.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVirendra%20Pratap%20Shahi%20lost%20both%20the%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Harshvardhan%20won%20the%20election%20from%20Maharajganj%20parliamentary%20seat.%20After%20the%20defeat%2C%20he%20left%20the%20local%20stages%20of%20Laxmipur%20and%20Maharajganj%20and%20became%20active%20in%20the%20Gorakhpur%20parliamentary%20constituency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20parting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20had%20a%20fall%20out%20with%20Harishankar%20Tiwari%20and%20they%20parted%20ways.%20Soon%20after%2C%20he%20joined%20Virendra.%20Strongman%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0leader%20Om%20Prakash%20Paswan%2C%20who%20became%20an%20MLA%20from%20Maniram%20on%20a%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20ticket%2C%20at%20that%20time%20developed%20a%20rift%20with%20his%20guru%20Mahant%20Avedyanath.%20He%20also%20joined%20Virendra.%20The%20trio%20remained%20together%20for%20several%20years%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20Gorakhpur.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPaswan%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20bomb%20attack%20on%20March%2025%2C%201996%20during%20a%20meeting%20in%20Bansgaon%2C%20just%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20incident%20was%20executed%20like%20a%20terrorist%20operation%2C%20killing%20seven%20people%20and%20injuring%2030.%20Four%20years%20later%2C%20in%201997%2C%20Virendra%20was%20murdered%20by%20gangster%20Sriprakash%20Shukla%20in%20Lucknow.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20his%20murder%2C%20Virendra%20was%20in%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20party%20supremo%20Mayawati%20was%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20losing%20the%20elections%20twice%2C%20Amarmani%20finally%20won%20in%201989%20but%20lost%20two%20subsequent%20elections%20in%201991%20and%201993%20to%20Akhilesh%20Singh.%20It%20was%20initially%20suspected%20that%20his%20political%20career%20would%20not%20last%20long%2C%20but%20after%20Akhilesh%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20focus%20shifted%20to%20the%20Maharajganj%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20Amarmani%20made%20a%20comeback%20by%20winning%20the%201996%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMurder%20and%20media%20attention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20the%20era%20of%20unstable%20governments.%20Amarmani%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20become%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20governments%20of%20Kalyan%20Singh%2C%20Ramprakash%20Gupta%20and%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20although%20he%20was%20not%20given%20important%20portfolios%20in%20any%20of%20them.%20But%20being%20in%20power%20gave%20him%20the%20opportunity%20to%20expand%20his%20clout.%20In%202002%2C%20he%20was%20in%20for%20a%20shock%20when%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20denied%20him%20a%20ticket.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%20when%20the%20BSP%2C%20in%20search%20of%20a%20Brahmin%20face%2C%20handed%20him%20the%20ticket.%20The%20party%20envisioned%20a%20lot%20of%20possibilities%20with%20Amarmani%2C%20who%20won%20the%20elections%20and%20got%20a%20cabinet%20berth.%20While%20BSP%20supremo%20Mayawati%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20avoid%20controversies%2C%20Amarmani%20was%20nevertheless%20embroiled%20in%20many.%20He%20also%20resorted%20to%20wanton%20misuse%20of%20power%20when%20it%20came%20to%20suppressing%20opponents.%20His%20arch-rival%20Akhilesh%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Kaushal%20Singh%20alias%20Munna%20Singh%20was%20charged%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20allegedly%20seized%20the%20Durga%20Oil%20Mill%20from%20a%20prominent%20businessman%20in%20Nautanwa%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20his%20office.%20Later%20he%20also%20got%20it%20allotted%20in%20his%20name.%20He%20attempted%20to%20take%20over%20the%20agricultural%20land%20in%20Nichlaul%20area%20as%20well%20and%20faced%20opposition%20from%20local%20farmers.%20His%20present%20residence%20in%20Gorakhpur%20was%20also%20allegedly%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20businessman%2C%20seized%20by%20Amarmani.%20In%20Nautanwa%2C%20the%20matter%20of%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20acquisition%20of%20land%20belonging%20to%20a%20former%20Army%20officer%20had%20reached%20the%20then%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20ears.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmarmani%20also%20set%20up%20half%20a%20dozen%20schools%20and%20colleges%20in%20Laxmipur%20area%20during%20this%20period.%20Several%20of%20his%20relatives%20are%20members%20of%20the%20management%20committees%20of%20these%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20used%20to%20organise%20poetry%20meets%20in%20the%20schools%20and%20colleges%20run%20by%20him.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20such%20event%20that%20he%20met%20the%20poet%20Madhumita%20Shukla.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fim-scared-got-death-threats-slain-poets-sister-nidhi-shukla-after-former-up-ministers-release%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20Scared%2C%20Got%20Death%20Threats%E2%80%99%3A%20Slain%20Poet%E2%80%99s%20Sister%20Nidhi%20Shukla%20After%20Former%20UP%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Release%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShukla%20was%20seven%20months%20pregnant%20when%20she%20was%20murdered%20in%20Lucknow.%20Amarmani%20was%20accused%20of%20the%20murder%20but%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20cover%20it%20up.%20The%20investigation%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department.%20When%20evidence%20was%20found%20against%20him%2C%20then%20CM%20Mayawati%20removed%20Amarmani%20from%20his%20ministerial%20post.%20But%20she%20also%20suspended%20two%20senior%20officers%20of%20the%20CBCID%20who%20had%20conducted%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20expelling%20Amarmani%20from%20post%2C%20the%20BSP%20supremo%20had%20remarked%20that%20he%20would%20be%20handed%20back%20the%20post%20if%20he%20was%20found%20to%20be%C2%A0%20innocent.%20The%20media%20coverage%20of%20the%20incident%20was%20a%20long%20and%20sustained%20one.%20Fingers%20were%20also%20pointed%20at%20the%20then%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20at%20the%20centre%20as%20the%20BJP%20was%20supporting%20the%20Mayawati%20government%20at%20the%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEventually%2C%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20incident%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20which%20arrested%20four%20people%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%2C%20including%20Amarmani%20and%20his%20wife%20Madhumani.%20All%20of%20the%20arrested%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20by%20a%20special%20CBI%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJail%20and%20afterwards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20being%20lodged%20in%20jail%2C%20Amarmani%20continued%20to%20exert%20significant%20influence%20in%20his%20constituency.%20He%20fought%20the%202007%20elections%20from%20prison%20on%20an%20SP%20ticket%20and%20won.%20Before%20this%20election%20an%20incident%20brought%20Amarmani%20close%20to%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20a%20clash%20in%20January%2C%202007%2C%20a%20youth%20was%20killed%20and%20the%20incident%20quickly%20took%20a%20communal%20turn.%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20Yuva%20Vahini%20jumped%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20the%20incident%20escalated.%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20state%20government%20arrested%20Adityanath.%20This%20sparked%20violence%20and%20arson%20not%20only%20in%20Gorakhpur%20but%20in%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20districts.%20Adityanath%20remained%20in%20Gorakhpur%20Divisional%20Jail%20for%20nine%20days.%20Amarmani%20was%20in%20the%20SP%20at%20the%20time%20and%20was%20contesting%20the%20elections%20from%20Laxmipur%20assembly%20from%20jail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20news%20of%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20proximity%20to%20Adityanath%20in%20jail%20became%20public%2C%20the%20former%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%20that%20he%20has%20been%20fighting%20communal%20forces%20throughout%20his%20life%20and%20will%20continue%20doing%20so.%20The%20statement%20was%20issued%20as%20he%20was%20worried%20that%20the%20news%20would%20upset%20the%20Muslims%20voters%20of%20Laxmipur.%20Amarmani%20won%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20his%20conviction%2C%20he%20got%20his%20son%2C%20Amanmani%20Tripathi%2C%20to%20contest%20the%202012%20elections.%20Amanmani%20lost.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Amanmani%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Sara%20Singh%20died%20in%20an%20alleged%20road%20accident.%20Sara%E2%80%99s%20mother%20accused%20Amanmani%20of%20murder.%20A%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Amanmani%20and%20he%20was%20arrested.%20A%20contractor%20also%20filed%20a%20case%20of%20kidnapping%20and%20assault%20against%20Amanmani%2C%20whose%20list%20of%20controversies%20soon%20grew.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160041%2FFM6ITmWVkAAS1YF.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160041%2FFM6ITmWVkAAS1YF.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160041%2FFM6ITmWVkAAS1YF-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160041%2FFM6ITmWVkAAS1YF-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAmanmani%20Tripathi%20(in%20green%20jacket)%20and%20others.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40amanmani_786%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%202012%20election%20defeat%2C%20the%20family%20had%20multiple%20setbacks.%20On%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%2C%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20encroachment%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20Durga%20Oil%20Mill%20in%20Nautanwa.%20He%20was%20also%20about%20to%20be%20ordered%20to%20vacate%20the%20Gorakhpur%20residence%2C%20but%20somehow%20the%20matter%20was%20resolved.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmanmani%20contested%20the%202017%20assembly%20elections%20while%20in%20jail.%20His%20sisters%20Tanushree%20and%20Alankrita%20put%20up%20a%20spirited%20election%20campaign.%20Amanmani%20won%20the%20polls%20and%20was%20elected%20an%20MLA.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20has%20appeared%20publicly%20alongside%20CM%20Adityanath%20quite%20a%20few%20times.%20Despite%20the%20travel%20ban%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Amanmani%20was%20found%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20pass%20issued%20so%20he%20could%20visit%20Badri%20Dham.%20That%20he%20was%20doing%20so%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20fake%20letter%20led%20to%20a%20case%20being%20registered%20against%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%2018th%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20elections%20held%20last%20year%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20ticket%20from%20the%20BSP%20but%20could%20not%20secure%20a%20win.%20He%20lost%20to%20the%20candidate%20nominated%20by%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20NISHAD%20Party%2C%20Rishi%20Tripathi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20in%20the%2011%20assembly%20elections%20held%20since%201980%2C%20Amarmani%20became%20MLA%20four%20times%20and%20his%20son%2C%20once.%20In%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Ajitmani%20contested%20but%20could%20not%20win.%20Despite%20being%20in%20jail%2C%20Amarmani%20has%20kept%20his%20family%20connected%20to%20his%20constituency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHospitals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmarmani%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20on%20October%2024%2C%202007%20by%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Dehradun.%20After%20the%20sentence%2C%20they%20remained%20lodged%20in%20Haridwar%20Jail%20for%20about%20five%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmarmani%20was%20transferred%20from%20Haridwar%20to%20Gorakhpur%20Divisional%20Jail%20in%20May%202012.%20In%20these%2010%20years%2C%20he%20has%20stayed%20in%20prison%20only%20for%2016%20months%20and%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20term%20in%20the%20private%20ward%20of%20BRD%20Medical%20College.%20Madhumani%20was%20also%20admitted%20in%20the%20private%20ward.%20Irrespective%20of%20who%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20stature%20saw%20no%20decline.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20it%20was%20the%20BSP%2C%20SP%20or%20BJP%20government%2C%20he%20has%20stayed%20in%20the%20hospital%20instead%20of%20jail%20in%20the%20name%20of%20medical%20treatments%20and%20has%20thus%20maintained%20a%20hold%20on%20the%20politics%20of%20his%20area.%20Owing%20to%20two%20sting%20operations%20and%20once%20on%20an%20order%20of%20the%20high%20court%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20stay%20in%20jail%20for%20some%20time%2C%20but%20even%20then%20he%20held%20meetings%20unhindered.%20Those%20who%20met%20him%20in%20jail%20say%20that%20he%20used%20to%20make%20calls%20to%20officers%20and%20leaders%20for%20favours%20for%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmarmani%20also%20got%20himself%20transferred%20from%20Haridwar%20to%20Gorakhpur%20citing%20appearance%20in%20hearings%20of%20cases%20registered%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Maharajganj%2C%20etc.%20At%20one%20point%20of%20time%2C%20more%20than%2040%20cases%20were%20registered%20against%20him%2C%20mostly%20in%20Maharajganj.%20He%20made%20sure%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20case%20hearings%20in%20Maharajganj%20and%20would%20arrive%20with%20pomp.%20A%20hoard%20of%20people%20flocked%20to%20meet%20him.%20In%20the%20affidavit%20filed%20in%20the%202007%20elections%2C%20he%20had%20provided%20details%20of%20six%20cases%20including%20murder%20and%20attempt%20to%20murder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20then%20CM%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20attended%20a%20programme%20at%20the%20BRD%20Medical%20College.%20After%20the%20event%20was%20over%2C%20his%20vehicle%20was%20seen%20going%20towards%20the%20private%20ward%2C%20where%20he%20met%20Amarmani.%20A%20lot%20of%20effort%20was%20made%20to%20hide%20the%20news%20but%20it%20caught%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20attention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20also%20rumoured%20that%20Amarmani%20made%20visits%20to%20his%20constituency%20and%20his%20residence%20from%20the%20private%20ward%20of%20BRD%20Medical%20College%20but%20this%20was%20never%20confirmed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20jail%20administration%20ordered%20his%20release%20on%20August%2024%20on%20his%20remission%20application%2C%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20signed%20the%20papers%20of%20necessary%20formalities%20and%20within%2024%20hours%20the%20jail%20administration%20went%20to%20BRD%20Medical%20College%20and%20completed%20the%20formalities%20of%20his%20release.%20The%20quickness%20clearly%20shows%20his%20level%20of%20penetration%20in%20the%20Adityanath%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20question%20is%20%E2%80%93%20what%20does%20the%20BJP%20gain%20from%20his%20release%3F%20Neither%20Amarmani%20nor%20his%20son%20nor%20any%20other%20relative%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Yet%20his%20one-and-a-half%20decade%20long%20closeness%20to%20Adityanath%20is%20well%20known.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20Amanmani%20calls%20the%20UP%20chief%20minister%20his%20patron.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20more%20than%20four%20decades%2C%20the%20political%20contest%20in%20the%20Nautanwa%20assembly%20constituency%20has%20been%20between%20Amarmani%20and%20Akhilesh%20Singh.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20the%20last%20election%20that%20someone%20outside%20these%20two%20camps%20recorded%20a%20win.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20duo%E2%80%99s%20poll%20campaigns%20have%20been%20quite%20interesting%20with%20each%20of%20them%20holding%20rallies%20at%20the%20same%20venue%20simultaneously%20and%20exchanging%20jibes%20for%20hours.%20Their%20supporters%20often%20end%20up%20getting%20into%20brawls%20while%20FIRs%20are%20registered%20on%20behalf%20of%20both%20sides.%20Nautanwa%E2%80%99s%20Janata%20Chowk%20used%20to%20be%20the%20electoral%20battlefield%20for%20both%20the%20camps.%20Journalists%20are%20often%20particularly%20eager%20to%20cover%20this%20region%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%20There%20is%20no%20village%20in%20the%20entire%20constituency%20where%20mobilisation%20is%20not%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20two.%20The%20region%20is%20still%20witness%20to%20such%20face-offs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20opined%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20use%20this%20attention%20and%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20political%20influence%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20bagged%20all%20the%20nine%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Gorakhpur-Basti%20division%20previously.%20Of%20the%20nine%20MPs%2C%20four%20are%20Brahmins%2C%20one%20Rajput%2C%20one%20Dalit%20and%20three%20belong%20to%20backward%20castes.%20R.P.N.%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Union%20minister%20in%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20last%20election%2C%20has%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Kushinagar%20seat.%20The%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20give%20him%20a%20ticket.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20possibility%20that%20three%20MPs%20will%20be%20denied%20tickets%20and%20the%20search%20is%20on%20for%20suitable%20candidates%20who%20will%20replace%20them.%20Such%20a%20scenario%20will%20open%20up%20opportunities%20for%20Amarmani%20and%20his%20family.%20Even%20if%20the%20party%20fails%20to%20find%20a%20place%20for%20him%2C%20he%20will%20prove%20useful%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarishankar%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20prominent%20Brahmin%20leader%20in%20Purvanchal%20and%20was%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Brahmin%20%3Cem%3Eshiromani%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20pioneer%20among%20Brahmins%20%E2%80%93%20died%20four%20months%20ago%20on%20May%2016.%20Both%20his%20sons%20Bhishma%20Shankar%20Tiwari%20and%20Vinay%20Shankar%20Tiwari%20as%20well%20as%20nephew%20Ganesh%20Shankar%20are%20politically%20active.%20Bhishma%20Shankar%20has%20been%20a%20two-time%20MP%20from%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%2C%20while%20Vinay%20Shankar%20Tiwari%20became%20an%20MLA%20from%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20seat%20in%202017%20but%20lost%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections.%20Bhishma%20Shankar%20also%20lost%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20twice%20while%20Ganesh%20Shankar%20has%20been%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Council.%20The%20whole%20family%20was%20in%20the%20BSP%20but%20after%20the%20assembly%20elections%20last%20year%20all%20of%20them%20joined%20the%20SP.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECM%20Adityanath%20has%20a%20long-standing%20political%20enmity%20with%20the%20Tiwari%20family.%20Many%20Brahmin%20leaders%20including%20the%20Tiwari%20clan%20members%20are%20engaged%20in%20trying%20to%20replace%20him.%20Several%20veteran%20leaders%20across%20party%20lines%20mourned%20his%20death%20but%20Adityanath%2C%20notably%2C%20did%20not%20express%20his%20condolences.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20speculated%20that%20Amarmani%20will%20be%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20CM%20Adityanath%20%E2%80%93%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EApne%3C%2Fem%3E%20Brahmin%20%3Cem%3Eshiromani%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20However%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20directly%20promote%20Amarmani%20or%20his%20family%20members%20because%20it%20will%20put%20it%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20the%20opposition.%20After%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpictures-phone-location-other-evidence-show-brij-bhushan-allegedly-making-advances%5C%22%3Ewas%20accused%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20female%20wrestlers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20move%20to%20bring%20forth%20a%20murder%20convict%20is%20likely%20to%20backfire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693535412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31161555%2FUntitled-design-8-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famarmani-tripathi-uttar-pradesh-adityanath-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20strongman's%20release%20has%20led%20to%20speculation%20on%20whether%20his%20long%20friendship%20with%20UP%20CM%20Adityanath%20will%20lead%20to%20his%20return%20in%20the%20politics%20of%2