0ceremony%20following%20Spain's%20win%20over%20England%20in%20the%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20Infantino%20said%20the%20behaviour%20of%20Spanish%20federation%20boss%20Rubiales%20had%20%26quot%3Bspoiled%26quot%3B%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20well-deserved%20celebrations%20for%20these%20magnificent%20champions%20were%20spoiled%20by%20what%20happened%20after%20the%20final%20whistle%2C%26quot%3B%20Infantino%20wrote%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20what%20continued%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20following%20days.%20This%20should%20never%20have%20happened.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFIFA%20opened%20disciplinary%20proceedings%20against%20Rubiales%20on%20August%2024%20--%20four%20days%20after%20the%20final%20in%20Sydney%20--%20and%20then%20provisionally%20suspended%20him%20from%20all%20football%20activities%20at%20national%20and%20international%20level%20for%2090%20days%2C%20while%20the%20investigation%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFIFA's%20disciplinary%20bodies%20immediately%20assumed%20their%20responsibility%20and%20took%20the%20necessary%20actions.%20The%20disciplinary%20proceedings%20will%20continue%20their%20legitimate%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Infantino%20who%20was%20at%20the%20trophy%20presentation%20after%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20our%20side%2C%20we%20should%20continue%20to%20focus%20on%20how%20to%20further%20support%20women%20and%20women's%20football%20in%20future%2C%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20pitch.%20Upholding%20true%20values%20and%20respecting%20the%20players%20as%20persons%20as%20well%20as%20for%20their%20fantastic%20performances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Spain's%20controversial%20Women's%20World%20Cup-winning%20coach%20Jorge%20Vilda%20is%20set%20to%20be%20forced%20out%20as%20the%20scandal%20engulfs%20the%20Spanish%20football%20federation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2080%20national%20team%20players%20are%20striking%20in%20protest%20until%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20federation%20(RFEF)%20is%20changed%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Rubiales'%20forcible%20kiss%20on%20the%20lips%20of%20midfielder%20Hermoso.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVilda%2C%20who%20last%20week%20applauded%20a%20speech%20in%20which%20Rubiales%20refused%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20position%20and%20railed%20against%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20feminism%26quot%3B%2C%20later%20criticised%20Rubiales'%20%26quot%3Binappropriate%20and%20unacceptable%26quot%3B%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20majority%20of%20Spain's%20coaching%20staff%20offered%20to%20step%20down%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Rubiales%20incident%2C%20Vilda%20did%20not%2C%20after%20Rubiales%20publicly%20announced%20the%20coach%20was%20in%20line%20for%20a%20new%20contract%20with%20a%20big%20pay%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20in%20Spain%20on%20Thursday%20said%20the%20RFEF's%20regional%20presidents%20had%20agreed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20Vilda's%20departure%20at%20a%20meeting%20Monday%2C%20although%20he%20is%20said%20to%20want%20another%20role%20at%20the%20federation%20if%20he%20leaves%20his%20current%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20say%20that%20(he%20has%20been%20sacked)%2C%20we%20haven't%20met%20with%20Vilda%2C%20until%20next%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20interim%20RFEF%20president%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pedro%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F93650-pedro-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPedro%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rocha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20have%2C%20we%20will%20explain%20the%20relevant%20news...%20first%20we%20have%20to%20listen%20and%20talk%2C%20that's%20the%20important%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERocha%20confirmed%20Spain%20men's%20coach%20Luis%20de%20la%20Fuente%2C%20who%20led%20the%20team%20to%20UEFA%20Nations%20League%20glory%20in%20June%2C%20would%20be%20staying%20--%20despite%20criticism%20in%20some%20quarters%20after%20he%20too%20applauded%20Rubiales'%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA