y%20that%20he%20had%20been%20hospitalized%20and%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20had%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeamsters%20Local%20767%20President%20Dave%20Reeves%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Ftexas%2Fnews%2Fchristopher-begley-ups-driver-dies-after-working-in-summer-heat%2F%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20is%20the%20second%20heat-related%20death%20of%20a%20UPS%20worker%20in%20North%20Central%20Texas%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%20and%20that%20multiple%20workers%20seek%20treatment%20at%20hospitals%20each%20week%20due%20to%20heat-related%20illnesses.%20The%20Teamsters%20union%20represents%20about%20340%2C000%20UPS%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Teamsters%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20angered%20by%20the%20untimely%20loss%20of%20two%20of%20our%20Teamster%20brothers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20union%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100064764308587%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02haoFHPuAf8QxgfedUJP7LpJh8SJpKwHZTkvpfx1U6qmtFjz4SiGqaQMyDBvUB5H1l%2F%3Fapp%3Dfbl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20Thursday.%20The%20post%20also%20referenced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Faug%2F28%2Fkroger-worker-dies-heat-temperature%5C%22%3ETony%20Rufus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Local%20667%20member%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20Kroger%20in%20Memphis%20and%20also%20died%20recently%20while%20working%20in%20extreme%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20losses%20are%20piercing%20and%20painful%20reminders%20that%20the%20protections%20that%20workers%20need%20are%20real%2C%20and%20employers%20need%20to%20step%20up%20and%20act%20accordingly%20when%20workers%20demand%20relief.%20Our%20members%20should%20have%20returned%20home%20safely%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscorching-heat-makes-delivery-jobs-dan