y%20but%20not%20irresolvable%20political%20issues%20that%20underlie.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThose%20are%20the%20key%20concerns%20I%20should%20raise%20today%20with%20the%20former%20home%20secretary%20whose%20knowledge%20of%20the%20Northeast%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Manipur%20in%20particular%20%E2%80%93%20is%20not%20just%20unsurpassed%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20unrivalled%2C%20Gopal%20Pillai.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMr.%20Pillai%2C%20on%20August%2029%2C%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20will%20convene%20for%20its%20Monsoon%20session%20for%20just%20one%20day.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20already%20clear%20that%20all%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20two%20of%20whom%20are%20ministers%2C%20seven%20are%20in%20fact%2C%20from%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20will%20boycott%20the%20session.%20At%20least%20two%20national%20newspapers%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20suggest%20that%20even%20the%2010%20Naga%20MPs%20may%20skip%20the%20session.%20In%20which%20case%2C%20beyond%20meeting%20constitutional%20requirements%2C%20what%20real%20purpose%20does%20this%20one-day%20session%20serve%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20really%20serves%20any%20purpose%20except%20to%20show%20that%20one%20instrument%20of%20the%20administrative%2C%20the%20constitutional%2C%20is%20still%20alive%20and%20kicking.%20Nothing%20more%20than%20that.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20fact%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20that%20a%20danger%20that%20if%20all%2020%20Naga%20and%20Kuki%20MLAs%20do%20not%20attend%20the%20session%2C%20it%20will%20be%20an%20all-Meitei%20session%20and%20that%20will%20deeply%20underline%20how%20deep%20and%20how%2C%20perhaps%20irreversible%2C%20the%20division%20in%20Manipur%20has%20become%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20not%20so%20sure%20yet%20whether%20the%20Naga%20MLAs%20would%20not%20attend%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlthough%2C%20two%20newspapers%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20suggested%20they%20wanted%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20do%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20it%20only%20sends%20a%20political%20signal%20of%20how%20isolated%20in%20one%20sense%20the%20Meiteis%20are%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5B%3Cstrong%3EEditor%E2%80%99s%20Note%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20the%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20including%20two%20cabinet%20ministers%2C%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assemblys-one-day-session-adjourned-after-11-minutes%5C%22%3E11-minute%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2010%20Naga%20MLAs%20did%20attend.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20that%20would%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20bring%20home%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20how%20deep%20and%20perhaps%20irreversible%20this%20divide%20is%20becoming.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20the%20division%20is%20very%20deep.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20irreversible%2C%20I%20would%20still%20wait%20to%20see%20how%20the%20developments%20take%20place%20on%20the%20various%20steps%20that%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20take%20%E2%80%93%20and%20whether%20they%20would%20take%20those%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20want%20very%20much%20to%20talk%20to%20you%20about%20the%20steps%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20and%20I%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20those%20steps%20in%20terms%20of%20different%20issues%20that%20occur%3A%20law%20and%20order%2C%20political%20issues%20and%20background%20issues.%20But%20before%20I%20come%20to%20that%2C%20let%20me%20ask%20you%20first%20for%20your%20assessment%20of%20the%20way%20governments%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Imphal%20%E2%80%93%20have%20so%20far%20handled%20this%20crisis.%20What%20is%20your%20assessment%20of%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20handling%20over%20almost%20the%20last%20four%20months%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20what%20we%20have%20to%20realise%20is%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20constitutional%20breakdown.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20been%20more%2C%20shall%20I%20say%2C%20explicit%20by%20its%20absence%20rather%20than%20its%20presence%20across%20all%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20areas.%20And%20to%20that%20extent%2C%20what%20was%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%A6%20one%20of%20the%20justices%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20mentioned%20that%20there%20is%20an%20apparent%20constitutional%20breakdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FoiwYwBRakTM%3Fsi%3DX0-h6jYhas592aai%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20should%20the%20chief%20minister%20be%20replaced%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20a%20political%20decision%20for%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20take.%20And%20I%20think%20with%20the%20governments%20being%20of%20the%20same%20%E2%80%93%20both%20BJP%20governments%20in%20the%20Centre%20and%20state%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20if%20they%20have%20not%20taken%20a%20decision%20so%20far%2C%20that%20they%20would%20take%20such%20a%20decision%20in%20the%20future.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20not-so-recent%20past%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20dismissed%20the%20Darbara%20Singh%20government%20in%20Punjab%20when%20she%20felt%20that%20they%20were%20failing%20to%20handle%20the%20situation%20vis-a-vis%20%5BSikh%20separatist%20leader%20Jarnail%20Singh%5D%20Bhindranwale.%20And%20that%20was%20a%20Congress%20government%20dismissed%20by%20a%20Congress%20prime%20minister.%20So%20the%20precedent%20exists.%20And%20I%20believe%20Nehru%20did%20that%20in%20his%20time%20as%20well.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurely%2C%20the%20interest%20of%20Manipur%20should%20be%20paramount%2C%20not%20the%20party%20interest%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Which%20is%20why%20I%20ask%E2%80%A6%20because%20clearly%2C%20this%20is%20the%20chief%20minister%20who%20has%20lost%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20Kuki%20people%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%2016%25%20%E2%80%93%20and%20several%20newspaper%20accounts%20say%2015%20of%20his%2032%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20including%20eight%20Meitei%20%E2%80%93%20have%20also%20publicly%20expressed%20a%20loss%20of%20confidence%20in%20him.%20So%20is%20he%20an%20obstacle%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20so%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20political%20party%20in%20power%20seeing%20it%20that%20way.%20Because%20if%20they%20saw%20it%2C%20they%20would%20then%20remove%20him.%20It%20might%20happen%20in%20the%20future%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20possible.%20But%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20government%20removing%20him%20because%20they%20feel%20that%20he%20serves%20a%20particular%20political%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20in%20his%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20said%20he%20was%20being%20retained%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9Ccooperating%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20was%20in%20terms%20of%20removing%20the%20chief%20secretary%20to%20moving%20the%20DGP%2C%20accepting%20Kuldiep%20Singh.%20But%20as%20a%20former%20home%20secretary%20who%20clearly%20puts%20the%20interest%20of%20Manipur%20before%20the%20politics%2C%20does%20cooperating%20make%20up%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20incompetent%20in%20restoring%20law%20and%20order%3F%20Does%20it%20make%20up%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20unacceptable%20to%2016%25%20of%20his%20population%20and%20perhaps%20pretty%20close%20to%2050%25%20of%20his%20own%20MLAs%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20question%20of%E2%80%A6%20one%20is%20of%20constitutional%20propriety%20and%20the%20other%20is%20the%20political%20aspects.%20And%20obviously%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20political%20issues%20have%20taken%20priority%20over%20constitutional%20aspects%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20that%20unfortunate%20in%20your%20eyes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unfortunate%2C%20yes%2C%20because%20it%20sends%20a%20wrong%20signal%20not%20just%20to%20Manipur.%20It%20sends%20a%20wrong%20signal%20to%20all%20the%20states%20in%20India%20and%20especially%20other%20states%20in%20the%20northeast%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20sending%20the%20wrong%20signal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think.%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20situation%20by%20the%20central%20government.%20In%20the%20speech%20that%20he%20made%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20the%20no-confidence%20and%20debate%20happened%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20spoke%20for%20two%20hours%20and%20he%20explained%20the%20present%20crisis%20in%20terms%20of%20an%20influx%20of%20illegal%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20Kuki%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Myanmar%20from%202021.%20Now%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20that%20is%20precisely%20how%20the%20Meitei%20believed%20the%20situation%20had%20arisen.%20But%20the%20Kuki%20have%20a%20very%20different%20explanation.%20Did%20the%20home%20minister%20make%20a%20mistake%20in%20only%20giving%20the%20explanation%20from%20one%20side%2C%20rather%20than%20from%20both%20sides%3F%20Has%20he%20ended%20up%20perhaps%20inadvertently%20making%20himself%20look%20partisan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20once%20you%20have%20supported%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20not%20dismissed%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20then%20you%20have%20to%20follow%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20has%20done.%20So%2C%20that%20was%20expected.%20Because%20if%20he%20had%20to%20follow%20any%20other%20narrative%2C%20then%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20dismiss%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20this%20follows%20from%20you%20saying%20that%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20sends%20a%20wrong%20message%20to%20Manipur%2C%20therefore%20the%20explanation%20%E2%80%93%20as%20far%20as%20the%20Kukis%20are%20concerned%20%E2%80%93%20sends%20the%20wrong%20message%20to%20them%20as%20well.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20I%20presume%20this%20is%20why%20the%20Kuki%20have%20responded%20so%20angrily%20towards%20the%20home%20minister%20said%20in%20Parliament.%20The%20list%20of%20Kuki%20organisations%20which%20have%20condemned%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20is%20pretty%20long%3A%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20Kuki%20Inpi%2C%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%2C%20the%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20and%20all%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20including%20seven%20who%20are%20from%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20own%20BJP.%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20this%20mean%20that%2C%20at%20the%20time%20when%20the%20home%20minister%20needed%20to%20reconcile%20the%20Kuki%20and%20the%20Meitei%2C%20and%20therefore%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Kuki%2C%20he%20ended%20up%20offending%20and%20annoying%20them%20instead%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20that%20is%20what%20I%20think%20the%20strategy%20was.%20So%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20you%20know%2C%20find%20anything%20new.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20therefore%20he%E2%80%99s%20just%20following%20that%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20explain%20that%20further%20Mr%20Pillai%3F%20You%20believe%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20to%20side%20with%20the%20Meiti%20and%20push%20the%20Kuki%20aside%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20done%20in%20actual%20practice%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20done.%20So%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20unfortunate%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20happened%20and%20the%20consequences%20are%20there%2C%20which%20we%20have%20seen.%20And%20now%20we%20have%2C%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20pieces%20and%20see%20where%20we%20take%20them%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20are%20saying%20something%20very%20important%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20only%20repeating%20it%20so%20the%20audience%20understands%20you%20fully.%20You%E2%80%99re%20actually%20saying%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20taken%20sides%20in%20the%20Meitei%20Kuki%20conflict%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20taken%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Meitei%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20truly%20unfortunate%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20unfortunate%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20politics%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1-300x100.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1-1024x341.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664686%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20(L)%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20had%20been%20home%20secretary%20and%20you%20saw%20this%20happening%2C%20what%20would%20you%20have%20said%20to%20the%20home%20minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20think%20first%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20you%20have%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%20And%20if%20you%20find%20that%20the%20state%20government%20%E2%80%93%20because%20law%20and%20order%20is%20the%20state%20subject%20%E2%80%93%20if%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20maintain%20that%2C%20then%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20take%20what%20action%20follows%20from%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20that%20if%20you%20were%20home%20secretary%20and%20the%20law%20and%20order%20was%20not%20under%20control%2C%20you%20would%20have%20said%20to%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20dispense%20with%20your%20chief%20minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes.%20I%20think%20if%20he%20could%20not%20control%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20went%20out%20of%20control%2C%20as%20it%20went%2C%20and%20you%20had%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20then%20I%20think%20you%20really%20need%2C%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20to%20have%20dismissed%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Because%20that%20I%20think%20was..%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20impose%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20but%20you%20could%20have%20got%20rid%20of%20him%20and%20brought%20in%20somebody%20else%20who%20you%20could%20try.%20And%20if%20he%20still%20failed%2C%20then%20the%20only%20other%20option%20is%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20I%E2%80%99ll%20sum%20up%20this%20bit%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20two%20very%20important%20things.%20One%2C%20that%20the%20strategy%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20using%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20is%20to%20take%20sides%20with%20the%20Meitei%20against%20the%20Kuki%2C%20is%20the%20wrong%20strategy%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20unfortunate.%20And%20secondly%2C%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20as%20chief%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20which%20follows%20from%20that%20strategy%20%E2%80%93%20is%20another%20terrible%20mistake.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it%20is.%20I%20think%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20handling.%20For%2079%20days%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20speak%20in%20public%20about%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20not%20a%20single%20syllable.%20Thereafter%2C%20if%20you%20count%20up%20the%20occasions%20when%20he%E2%80%99s%20spoken%20about%20Manipur%2C%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20total%20of%20under%2010%20minutes.%20Which%20means%20in%20nearly%20four%20months%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20has%20spent%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%20speaking%20about%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20crises%20India%20faces.%20As%20a%20former%20home%20secretary%2C%20what%20do%20you%20make%20of%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20left%20it%20to%20the%20home%20minister%20to%20take%20a%20call.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20one%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%2C%20again%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20he%20has%20taken%2C%20He%20thinks%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20handling%20it%2C%20and%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20interfere%20with%20what%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20doing.%20Therefore%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20kept%20his%20%E2%80%93%20shall%20I%20say%20%E2%80%93%20minimal%20approach%20rather%20than%20intervene%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiven%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20crisis%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20carried%20on%20for%20months%2C%20was%20the%20prime%20minister%20right%20to%20leave%20this%20entirely%20to%20the%20home%20minister%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20a%20difficult%20call%20for%20me%20to%20make%20is%20that.%3Cspan%3E%20I%3C%2Fspan%3Et%E2%80%99s%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%2C%20he%20takes%20the%20call.%20He%E2%80%99s%20politically%20very%20astute.%20So%20he%E2%80%99s%20taken%20the%20call%2C%20I%20think%20very%20deliberately%20and%20in%20a%20measured%20way.%20So%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20see%20how%20things%20pan%20out%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%2C%20to%20see%20whether%20that%20call%20was%20right%20or%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlier%2C%20when%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20you%20said%20he%20has%20consciously%20put%20BJP%20politics%20ahead%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20requirements.%20That%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20is%20also%20true%20of%20Mr%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20see%20how%20things%20go%E2%80%A6%20the%20matter%20is%20already%20before%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%A6%20the%20issues%20which%20are%20coming%20%5Bup%5D%2C%20I%20think%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20see%20how%20it%20pans%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPractically%20everyone%20I%E2%80%99ve%20spoken%20to%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20the%20last%20four%20months%2C%20I%20think%20I%E2%80%99ve%20done%20about%2030-31%20interviews%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20these%20guests%20were%20Meiti%2C%20Kuki%2C%20Meitei%20Pangal%20or%20Naga%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20all%20said%20that%20they%20feel%20let%20down%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Many%20have%20said%20they%20think%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20turned%20their%20back%20on%20them.%20One%20of%20them%20even%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20see%20the%20prime%20minister.%E2%80%9D%20Then%2C%20are%20people%20in%20Manipur%20justified%20in%20feeling%20and%20thinking%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%20I%20think%20you%20are%E2%80%A6%20In%20a%20state%2C%20you%20are%20depending%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20solve%20all%20your%20local%20problems.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20solved%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20And%20I%20think%20you%20cannot%20expect%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%20especially%20as%20complex%20and%20complicated%20as%20Manipur%2C%20just%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20intervening.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20which%20you%20have%20to%20solve%20yourself%2C%20and%20I%20think%20if%20you%20are%20not%20able%20to%20solve%20it%2C%20there%20are%20other%20constitutional%20remedies%20%E2%80%93%20which%20of%20course%2C%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20%E2%80%93%20but%20you%20have%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20by%20discussion%20and%20dialogue%20among%20the%20groups%20in%20Manipur%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20last%20question%20about%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Many%20people%20say%2C%20many%20people%20in%20Manipur%2C%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20most%20popular%20person%20in%20the%20country%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20by%20far%20the%20most%20powerful.%20Were%20he%20to%20take%20an%20initiative%2C%20were%20he%20to%20fly%20in%20for%20a%20day%2C%20were%20he%20to%20invite%20civil%20society%20organisations%20to%20meet%20him%2C%20he%20would%20give%20a%20message%20that%20he%20personally%20cares%2C%20and%20that%20would%20encourage%20people%20to%20talk%2C%20perhaps%20to%20reconcile.%20That%20initiative%20needed%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20him.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20any%20prime%20minister%2C%20in%20a%20situation%20of%20this%20nature%2C%20needs%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20people%20because%20they%20are%20all%20his%20%5Bpeople%5D%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20all%20of%20India.%20And%20therefore%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20reach%20out%20at%20the%20earliest%20when%20the%20situation%20%5Bdemands%5D%E2%80%A6%20unless%20there%20is%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20intelligence%20briefings%20and%20the%20other%20reports