uman%20touch%20is%20very%2C%20very%20critical%20for%20them%20%E2%80%93%20that%20somebody%20cares.%20And%20it%20would%20make%20a%20tremendous%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBy%20failing%20to%20reach%20out%2C%20by%20failing%20to%20give%20that%20human%20touch%20%E2%80%93%20to%20use%20your%20words%20that%20somebody%20cares%20%E2%80%93%20and%20let%E2%80%99s%20be%20honest%20Mr%20Modi%20is%20very%20good%20at%20doing%20it%20when%20he%20wants%20to%2C%20has%20he%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Manipur%2C%20been%20irresponsible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%2C%20you%20see%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20that%20he%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20wrong%20call%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20that%E2%80%99s%20for%20him%20to%20take%2C%20because%20he%20said%20he%20would%20have%20left%20it%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20to%20take%20the%20decision.%20He%20may%20have%20felt%20that%20his%20interfering%20would%20undermine%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20position%E2%80%A6%20I%20mean%20any%20number%20of%20reasons%20there%20could%20be.%20And%20he%20sort%20of%20felt%20that%20his%20interference%2C%20at%20the%20early%20stages%2C%20may%20have%20been%20wrong.%20I%20personally%20feel%20that%20his%20intervention%20would%20have%20had%20a%20very%20salutary%20effect%20on%20the%20situation.%20But%20that%20is%20my%20view%20%E2%80%93%20others%20may%20feel%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely.%20So%20in%20your%20personal%20opinion%2C%20he%20took%20the%20wrong%20call%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20personal%20opinion%2C%20he%20should%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20people%20in%20Manipur%2C%20even%20perhaps%20visited%20Manipur.%20Or%20at%20least%2C%20he%20should%20have%20called%20everybody%20over.%20The%20least%20he%20could%20have%20done%20was%20to%20call%20everybody%20over%20to%20Delhi%20for%20talks%20in%20the%20first%20week%20or%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%