n%20of%20duty.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20it%E2%80%99s%20happened%20in%20this%20sort%20of%20case.%20Second%2C%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20people%20know%20with%20whom%20the%20arms.%20You%20should%20by%20now%20have%20been%20raiding%20houses%20across%20Manipur%20to%20recover%20these%20arms%2C%20which%20has%20not%20happened.%20And%20you%20put%20drop%20boxes%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20ridiculous%20situation%2C%20that%20after%20the%20arms%20are%20looted%2C%20you%20put%20drop%20boxes%20in%20different%20parts%20and%20expect%20the%20people%20who%20have%20looted%20the%20arms%20to%20come%20and%20drop%20the%20weapons%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20one%20aspect.%20Second%2C%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20start%20slowly.%20Initially%2C%20yes%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-300x221.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-1024x754.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGun%20drop%20box%20placed%20in%20Imphal%20Manipur.%20Authorities%20are%20asking%20people%20to%20voluntarily%20return%20snatched%20and%20looted%20weapons.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20I%20interrupt%20that%20point%20before%20you%20come%20to%20the%20second%20aspect%3F%20A%20corollary%20of%20what%20you%20said%20is%20that%20people%20are%2