20we%20have%20not%20faced%20before.%20But%20in%20all%20cases%20which%20have%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20UP%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Bihar%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Kerala%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20%5Banywhere%20else%5D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20State%20has%20responded%20very%20quickly.%20In%20any%20riot%20situation%2C%20the%20state%20responds%20very%20quickly%20and%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20respond%20quickly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20real%20failure.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%93%20officers%20also%20%E2%80%93%20are%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20where%20Manipur%20is%20a%20clear%20outlier.%20We%20haven%E2%80%99t%20responded%20quickly.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20know%20what%20we%20should%20be%20doing%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20doing%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20hard%20to%20move%20further%2C%20but%20academically%2C%20I%20will.%20I%20imagine%2C%20side%20by%20side%20with%20tackling%20law%20and%20order%20%E2%80%93%20which%20as%20you%20pointed%20out%2C%20is%20being%20done%20ineffectively%2C%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20done%20at%20all%20%E2%80%93%20the%20government%20also%20needs%20to%20turn%20its%20attention%20to%20the%20very%20difficult%2C%20intractable%2C%20political%20issues.%20Are%20the%20talks%20that%20are%20happening%20with%20the%20COCOMI%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20from%20the%20Meiti%20side%2C%20and%20with%20the%20ITLF%20from%20the%20Kuki%20side%2C%20the%20right%20way%20of%20tackling%20this%20political%20issue%3F%20Or%20should%20the%20government%20be%20reaching%20out%20through%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%2C%20perhaps%20through%20highly%20regarded%20individuals%20who%20both%20sides%20respect%20like%20for%20example%2C%20Ratan%20Thiyam%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20the%20government%20has%20started%2C%20I%20think%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20fact%2C%20that%20the%20dialogues%20have%20started%20even%20though%2C%20it%E