tion%20is%20restored%20and%20people%20can%20go%20about%20their%20normal%20lives.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20you%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20as%20you%20said%2C%20sounds%20so%20obvious.%20Why%20is%20it%20not%20being%20done%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%20Though%20I%20must%20say%20that%20in%20the%20first%20instance%20last%20week%2C%20they%20just%20started%20posting%20All%20India%20Service%20tribal%20officers%20to%20the%20hill%20districts%2C%20so%20three%20or%20four%20officers%20have%20been%20posted.%20I%20mean%20the%20first%20steps%2C%20maybe%20they%20are%20starting%20to%20realise%20that%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20me%20something.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20things%20that%20need%20to%20be%20done%20in%20terms%20of%20restoring%20law%20and%20order%2C%20rehabilitation%2C%20getting%20the%20administration%20functioning%2C%20empowering%20district%20magistrates%20so%20that%20they%20can%20temporarily%20appoint%20people.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20made%20it%20seem%20so%20simple%20and%20obvious%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20astounded%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20happening%2C%20but%20leave%20that%20aside.%20Should%20the%20chief%20minister%20be%20removed%20to%20facilitate%20all%20of%20this%20happening%3F%20Is%20he%20an%20obstacle%3F%20Is%20that%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20happening%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20talked%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20you%20know%2C%20some%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20administration%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20say%2C%20But%20I%20would%20have%20expected%20that%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%20because%20the%20MHA%20has%20a%20very%20special%20relationship%20with%20states%20in%20the%20Northeast.Hhistorically%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20the%3Cem%3E%20maa-baap%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mother%20and%20father)%20figure.%20So%20I%20would%20have%20expected%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20