E2%80%93%20either%20as%20a%20state%20or%20the%20central%20level%20%E2%80%93%20to%20handle%20those%20warning%20signs.%20If%20%5Bany%20steps%5D%20were%20%5Btaken%5D%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20disclosed%20publicly.%20But%20the%20warning%20signs%20are%20there.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20talked%20to%20people%20in%20the%20administration%20in%20Manipur%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20talked%20to%20people%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20so%20on.%20Everybody%20says%20the%20warning%20signs%20were%20there.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20saw%20that%2C%20everyone%20knew%20there%20were%20warning%20signs.%20No%20one%20acted.%20You%20can%20only%20blame%20yourself.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20background%20issues.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20go%20through%20them%20one%20by%20one.%20First%20I%E2%80%99ll%20take%20up%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Meitei%2C%20then%20I%E2%80%99ll%20come%20to%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Kuki%2C%20just%20for%20simplicity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Meitei%20believe%20that%20the%20Kuki%20are%20involved%20in%20poppy%20cultivation%20and%20in%20illegal%20drug%20trade.%20What%20we%20know%20from%20the%20interview%20that%20Thounaojam%20Brinda%20has%20given%20me%20and%20she%E2%80%99s%20given%20it%20also%20to%20other%20%5Boutlets%5D.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20alleges%2C%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20protecting%20a%20drug%20lord%20who%20is%20a%20BJP%20functionary%20and%20his%20wife%20too%2C%20she%20alleges%2C%20is%20involved.%20So%20is%20this%20charge%20made%20by%20the%20Meitei%20against%20the%20Kuki%2C%20pointing%20fingers%20only%20in%20one%20direction%3F%20Or%20are%20they%20all%20involved%20in%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20everybody%20is%20involved.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%2C%20I%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20there%20in%20the%20past%20%E2%80%93%20the%20drugs%2C%20both%20within%20Manipur%20as%20well%20as%20outside.%20Manipur%20has%20a%20history%20of%20drug%20problems%2C%20starting%20from%20HIV%2C%20then%20the%20whole%20community%20got%20together%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20sort%20of%20tackle%20that.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20which%20is%20there.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20its%E2%80%A6%20Everybody%20is%20involved%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fact.%20And%20how%20they%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20tackle%20it%20is%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%E2%80%A6%20all%20these%20people%20are%20now%20to%20see%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20PMLA%20and%20so%20on%2C%20money%20laundering%20etc.%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20big%20money.%20Poppy%20cultivation%2C%20the%20cultivation%20by%20the%20farmers%20is%20what%3F%20Maybe%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20drug%20trade.%20So%20the%20poppy%20cultivation%20itself%20is%20small%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20large%20inflow%20of%20drugs%20and%20chemicals%20coming%20across.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20partly%20because%20again%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%E2%80%A6%20because%20mainstream%20media%20in%20India%20has%20not%20covered%20a%20civil%20war%20which%20is%20going%20on%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20mean%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%2C%20you%20know%E2%80%A6.%20we%E2%80%99ve%20had%20coverage%20once%2C%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20the%20air%20raid%20on%20Aizawl%2C%20those%20big%20headlines%E2%80%A6%20that%20%5Bthe%20air%20force%20was%5D%20used%20against%20their%20own%20citizens.%20The%20Myanmar%20government%20is%20bombing%20away%20left%2C%20right%20and%20centre%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20have%20these%20refugees%20coming%20in%20to%20India.%20And%20I%20think%20it%20is%20very%20important%20for%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20have%2C%20if%20not%20a%20refugee%20policy%2C%20at%20least%20keep%20a%20complete%20tab%20on%20who%20is%20coming%20across%20the%20border%20and%20put%20them%20into%20refugee%20camps.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20serious%20is%20the%20influx%20of%20illegal%20Kuki%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%3F%20All%20the%20newspaper%20reports%20I%E2%80%99ve%20read%20suggest%20that%20a%20survey%20done%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20put%20the%20numbers%20that%20entered%20Manipur%20under%203%2C000.%20Something%20like%2045%2C000%20have%20gone%20to%20Mizoram.%20How%20worrying%20is%20an%20influx%20of%203%2C000%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20being%20exaggerated%20to%20point%20fingers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20one%2C%20since%20the%20actual%20thing%20has%20not%20been%20done%2C%20I%20would%20be%20skeptical%20about%20the%20numbers.%20I%20think%2C%20the%20figures%20in%20Mizoram%20are%20slightly%20more%20than%2045%2C000%20etc%2C.%20Maybe%20%5Bin%20Manipur%5D%203%2C000%20is%20slightly%20on%20the%20lower%20side.%20It%20may%20be%20higher%2C%20maybe%2010%2C000%2C%20maybe%20more.%20But%20these%20are%20refugees.%20See%2C%20nobody%20likes%20to%20leave%20his%20village%20and%20come%20across%20just%20carrying%20whatever%20is%20on%20the%20back%20of%20their%20head%20to%20another%20place%20unless%20there%20dire%20straits%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20So%20it%20is%20important%20for%20you%20to%20say%20that%20these%20are%20refugees%2C%20like%20when%20you%20know%20Bangladesh%E2%80%A6%20they%20had%20a%20problem%20in%20East%20Pakistan%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10%20million%20came.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10%20million%20came.%20So%20we%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem.%E2%80%9D%20The%20refugee%20camps%20were%20set%20up%2C%20you%20document%20them%2C%20you%20fingerprint%20them%2C%20you%20photograph%20them%2C%20you%20can%20do%20all%20that%20you%20want%2C%20and%20they%20remain%20as%20documented%20refugees%20in%20refugee%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20saying%20a%20very%20important%20thing.%20These%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20come%2C%20whether%20they%E2%80%99re%20three%2C%20four%2C%20five%20or%20ten%20thousand%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20fleeing%20from%20terror%20in%20Myanmar.%20Obviously%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20they%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20their%20home.%20But%20they%20are%20not%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20make%20a%20living%20forever%20in%20India.%20There%20is%20a%20distinction%20to%20be%20made%20between%20refugees%20from%20militant%20Myanmar%20terror%20and%20people%20who%20have%20come%20to%20make%20a%20home%20in%20India.%20They%E2%80%99re%20the%20first%2C%20not%20the%20second.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%20and%20therefore%20once%20you%20document%20these%20refugees%2C%20he%20never%20becomes%20an%20illegal%20migrant%20because%20he%20always%20remains%20a%20refugee.%20Then%20you%20have%20to%20take%20up%20with%20the%20government%20of%20Myanmar%20to%20send%20them%20back%20at%20some%20point%20of%20time%2C%20when%20the%20situation%20is%20%5Bfine%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20something%20else%20flows%20from%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying.%20I%E2%80%99m%20talking%20now%20both%20about%20what%20you%20said%20earlier%20about%20the%20poppy%20trade%20and%20also%20about%20these%20refugees.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20finger%20has%20been%20pointed%20almost%20exclusively%2C%20at%20the%20Kuki%2C%20but%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20both%20sides%20are%20involved%2C%20in%20the%20poppy%20trade%20and%20the%20drug%20trade%20%E2%80%93%20Brinda%E2%80%99s%20interview%20makes%20that%20clear%2C%20the%20involvement%20on%20the%20Meitei%20side%20goes%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20chief%20minister.%20And%20again%2C%20you%20are%20saying%2C%20as%20regards%20these%20refugees%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20coming%20to%20permanently%20settle%2C%20they%20are%20fleeing%20for%20fear%20of%20their%20lives%20and%20they%20want%20to%20go%20back%20one%20day.%20Again%2C%20the%20finger%20is%20pointed%20to%20the%20Kuki%2C%20and%20said%20you%E2%80%99re%20deliberately%20changing%20the%20demography%20%E2%80%93%20they%E2%80%99re%20not.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20the%20demography%20will%20change.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20that%20numbers%20yet.%20But%20remember%2C%20all%20the%20time%20we%E2%80%99re%20talking%20of%20%E2%80%9CKukis%E2%80%9D%20but%20the%20Kukis%2C%20they%20are%20also%20the%20Zomis%2C%20they%20are%20the%20Chins%20%E2%80%93%20all%20are%20different.%20I%20mean%20we%20look%20at%20it%E2%80%A6%20the%20Kuki%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20the%20Zo%20and%20the%20Chins.%20They%20fought%2C%20you%20know%2C%20in%20the%20late%2090s%2C%20the%20Kukis%20and%20the%20Paites%2C%20they%20had%20a%20huge%20fight%20where%2C%20you%20know%2C%20thousands%20were%20killed.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20see%20that%20different%20ethnic%20tribes%20from%20across%20the%20border%20are%20coming.%20Whether%20some%20of%20them%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20drug%20trade%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20for%E2%80%A6%20its%20open.%20And%20if%20I%20am%20coming%20here%20and%20I%20am%2C%20shall%20I%20say%20not%20put%20in%20a%20refugee%20camp%2C%20where%20I%E2%80%99m%20housed%20as%20a%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Refugees%2C%20they%20give%20you%20a%20refugee%20status%2C%20stamp%2C%20etc.%20Then%20you%20are%20on%20your%20own.%20And%20when%20you%20are%20on%20your%20own%2C%20I%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20some%20of%20them%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20this%20illegal%20drug%20trade%20because%20they%20will%20then%E2%80%A6%20they%20have%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20administration%2C%20the%20system%20needs%20to%20respond%20more%20effectively%20to%20this%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20refugees%20remain%20refugees.%20And%20this%20is%20again%20another%20area%20where%20the%20state%20administration%20has%20failed.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20think%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen.%20Even%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20they%20are%20officially%20saying%20these%20are%20refugees.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20housed%20in%20camps%2C%20some%20of%20them%20are%20housed%20with%20individual%20families%2C%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%2C%20you%20know%2C%20their%20relatives%2C%20their%20Chins%2C%20their%20communities%2C%20the%20same%20places%20and%20so%20on.%20But%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20given%20a%20single%20pie%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eto%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20to%20help%20in%E2%80%A6%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20are%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20refugees%20who%20have%20come%20across%2C%20we%20got%20the%20names%20we%E2%80%99ve%20got%20this%20thing%2C%20we%20give%20you%20all%20%5Binformation%5D.%20We%20are%20providing%20funds%20from%20our%20state%20budget%2C%20help%20us%20with%20some%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-1024x675.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-628160%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20image%3A%20A%20Zawlsei%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Aizawl.%20The%20camp%20serves%20as%20home%20to%20Myanmarese%20who%20fled%20the%20military%20persecution%20in%20their%20country.%20Photo%3A%20Sushila%20Sahay%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Mizoram%20government%20asked%20for%20Rs%2010%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20vast%20sum%20of%20money.%20I%20believe%20they%20were%20given%20Rs%203%20crore%2C%20eventually%2C%20after%20a%20two%20month%20delay.%20But%20another%20aspect%20of%20that%20is%20that%20there%20are%20some%2014%2C000%20Manipuri%20refugees%20in%20Mizoram%20and%20the%20Manipur%20government%20has%20done%20nothing%20whatsoever%20to%20help%20them.%20I%20mean%20it%20could%20have%20sent%20money%20to%20Mizoram%20to%20help%20them.%20Those%20people%20are%20surviving%20on%20either%20Mizo%20government%20largesse%20or%20Mizo%20civil%20society%20charity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20third%20background%20factor%20is%20this%20charge%20made%20against%20the%20Kuki%20about%20encroaching%20on%20forest%20life.%20How%20accurate%20is%20it%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20a%20misunderstanding%2C%20as%20the%20Kuki%20claim%2C%20of%20the%20slash-and-burn%20style%20of%20cultivation%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20complicated%20issue%20because%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20at%E2%80%A6%20The%20hill%20areas%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20forest%20areas.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20been%20doing%20slash-and-burn%20%5Bstyle%20of%20cultivation%5D%20for%20centuries.%20You%20also%20have%20in%20Manipur%2C%20I%20mean%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%2C%20you%20have%20the%20forest%20rights%20for%20tribals%20who%20have%20been%20there.%20That%E2%80%99s%20one%20aspect%20of%20what%20they%20do.%20There%E2%80%99s%20now%20also%20forests%20which%20are%20to%20be%20preserved%20as%20forests%20and%20not%20to%20be%20%5Bused%20for%5D%20slash-an-%20burn%20%5Bstyle%20of%20agriculture%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20yet%20to%20examine%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20new%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%20which%20was%20passed%20in%20Parliament%20in%20their%20previous%20session%2C%20where%20the%20government%20has%20got%20the%20right%20to%20say%20this%20is%20a%20forest%20and%20this%20is%20not%20a%20forest%2C%20so%20there%20are%20some%20areas%20on%20which%20there%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20gray%20area.%20Those%20have%20not%20yet%20got%20implemented.%20Again%2C%20when%20the%20Manipur%20government%20starts%20to%20implement%20the%20new%20Forest%20Act%2C%20and%20declare%20a%20particular%20area%20as%20non-forest%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%2C%20it%20will%20create%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20Manipur%20government%20again%20wrongly%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20the%20Kuki%20and%20claiming%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20encroaching%2C%20when%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20style%20of%20cultivation%20the%20Kukis%20use%3F%20Is%20there%20a%20mistake%20being%20made%20in%20pointing%20a%20finger%20at%20them%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20both.%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20one%20slash-and-burn%20cultivation%20which%20is%20normal.%20Then%2C%20you%20also%20have%20some%20encroachment%20which%20is%20taking%20place.%20People%20encroach%20anywhere%2C%20I%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20across%20the%20world%E2%80%A6.%20When%20any%20public%20area%20is%20available%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20you%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20that%20the%20charge%20of%20encroachment%20may%20not%20be%20wrong%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20exaggerated.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20exaggerated%20but%20I%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20there%20was%20not%20some%20encroachment%20into%20the%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20human%20nature%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20on%20the%20three%20background%20issues%20we%E2%80%99ve%20discussed%20%E2%80%93%20refugees%3B%20involvement%20in%20drug%20trade%20and%20poppy%20cultivation%3B%20and%20encroachment%20in%20forest%20areas%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20an%20element%20of%20exaggeration%20when%20the%20finger%20is%20pointed%20uniquely%20and%20exclusively%20at%20the%20Kuki.%20Both%20sides%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20drug%20trade.%20The%20refugees%20are%20actually%20refugees%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20coming%20to%20change%20the%20demography%20%E2%80%93%20they%20will%20go%20back%2C%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20understood.%20And%20as%20regards%20encroachment%2C%20there%20is%20some%20encroachment%20happening%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20exaggerated.%20Is%20that%20correct%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20actual%20ground%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%2C%20then%2C%20come%20to%20the%20two%20critical%20issues%2C%20that%20are%20perhaps%20the%20last%20part%20of%20this%20interview.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20the%20Meitei%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20real%20concern%20is%20what%20they%20call%20the%20%E2%80%9Cland%20imbalance%E2%80%9D.%20And%20they%20think%20it%20should%20be%20resolved%20in%20terms%20of%20giving%20them%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status.%20Do%20you%20believe%20%E2%80%93%20given%20your%20understanding%20of%20Manipur%20and%20its%20complexities%20%E2%80%93%20that%20ST%20status%20is%20the%20right%20way%20of%20addressing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cland%20imbalance%E2%80%9D%3F%20Or%20are%20there%20other%20ways%20that%20could%20be%20equally%20efficacious%20but%20less%20controversial%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20so.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%2C%20even%20among%20the%20Meiteis%E2%80%A6%20there%20was%20earlier%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20almost%2070%25%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20ST%20status.%20Now%20they%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%2050-50%20after%20these%20clashes%20and%20so%20on.%20Land%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%20And%20the%20Meiteis%20have%20a%20genuine%20grievance%2C%20if%20I%20may%20put%20it%20that%20way.%20Primarily%2C%20again%20psychologically%2C%20that%20you%20know%20people%20from%20the%20hills%20can%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20but%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20hills.%20And%20I%20think%20this%20is%20where%20I%20think%20political%20statesmanship%20from%20both%20sides%20involved%20%5Bis%20required%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20certain%20land%20hunger%20there%20fore%20everybody.%20%5BIn%20the%20Valley%2C%5D%20it%20is%20very%20thickly%20populated%20and%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eless%20populated%20%5Bin%20the%20hills%5D%2C%20but%20of%20course%2C%20you%20also%20have%20forest%20areas..%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20apple%20to%20apple.%20So%20you%20need%20some%20element%20of%20political%20compromise%20by%20which%20the%20Meiteis%20also%20can%20have%20some%20access%20to%20land%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20for%20certain%20purposes.%20You%20can%20have%20a%20restriction%2C%20you%20can%20say%2C%20ceiling%20will%20be%205%25%20or%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20area%20for%20A%2CB%2CC%20purposes%20etc%2C.%20Some%20of%20it%2C%20there%20have%20been%20discussions%20in%20the%20past%20with%20the%20Hill%20Area%20Council%20in%20terms%20of%20%E2%80%93%20for%20industrial%20purposes%2C%20for%20setting%20up%20industrial%20parks%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%3B%20for%20the%20Meiteis%20who%20come%20and%20settle%20down%2C%20who%20are%20working%20government%20servants.%20Under%20the%20Manipur%20Public%20Service%20Commission%2C%20they%20get%20recruited%2C%20then%20you%20can%20get%20them%20posted%20to%20the%20hills%2C%20you%20might%20marry%20somebody%20there%20and%20you%20want%20to%20settle%20down%20there.%20Then%20you%20should%20be%20allowed%20%5Bto%20buy%20land%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20permission%20from%20hill%20councils%20is%20already%20available%20but%20it%2C%20I%20gather%2C%20is%20given%20very%20grudgingly.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20given%20grudgingly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20the%20land%20imbalance%2C%20that%20with%20the%20political%20initiative%20taken%20by%20sensible%20farsighted%20politicians%20can%20be%20very%20easily%20reserved.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20people%20have%20to%20realise%20that%20it%20is%20an%20issue.%20You%20have%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20Meiteis%20have%20a%20problem.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20brush%20it%20aside%2C%20under%20the%20carpet.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hills%20are%20ours%2C%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20give%20you%20a%20cent%20of%20it.%E2%80%9D%20I%20think%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20that%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20corollary%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20this%20can%20be%20resolved%20without%20necessarily%20giving%20the%20Meitei%20ST%20status.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20you%20need%20a%20far-sighted%20politician%20who%20takes%20the%20initiative.%20And%20that%20means%20someone%20has%20to%20stick%20their%20neck%20out%2C%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20you%20do%20when%20you%20take%20an%20initiative%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20Meiteis%E2%80%A6%20a%20lot%20of%20responsible%20citizens%20also%20say%20that%20the%20current%20definition%20of%20STs%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20the%20Meiteis.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20Vaishnavite%20Brahmins%3B%20some%20of%20them%2C%20of%20course%2C%20looking%20back%20to%20their%20old%20indigenous%20faith%2C%20in%20which%20case%2C%20they%20are%2C%20you%20know%2C%20shall%20have%20more%20akin%20to%20STs.%20But%20today%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20where%20they%20are%20now%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20education%2C%20their%20social%20position%2C%20lack%20of%20discrimination%2C%20nobody%20discriminates%20against%20Meiteis%3B%20the%20educational%20levels%E2%80%A6%20All%20the%20things%20which%20ST%20commission%20would%20actually%20look%20at%20to%20see%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20missing%20in%20their%20case.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20missing.%C2%A0So%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20they%20would%20get%20from%20the%20ST%20commission%2C%20an%20ST%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20what%20you%20are%20saying%20is%20that%20the%20land%20hunger%20of%20the%20Meitei%20can%20be%20resolved%20if%20a%20far-sighted%20politician%20would%20take%20the%20initiative.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20require%20ST%20status%20but%20a%20political%20decision%20taken%20by%20a%20sensible%20politician.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20problem.%20Such%20a%20politician%20is%20missing.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20also%20from%20the%20other%20side%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20the%20hill%20areas%20also%2C%20the%20people%20must%20also%20be%20a%20little%20accommodative.%20If%20they%20see%20that%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20accommodation%20%5Bis%20taking%20place%5D%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Meitei%20politicians%20will%20also%20respond%20positively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20last%20issue.%20The%20Kuki%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20last%20four%20months%2C%20are%20demanding%20separate%20administration.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20cannot%20live%20with%20the%20Meitei%20any%20longer%20after%20what%E2%80%99s%20happened.%20And%20this%20is%20a%20separate%20administration%20means%2C%20either%20a%20separate%20state%20or%20a%20union%20territory%20status.%20Now%2C%20if%20you%20were%20home%20secretary%2C%20this%20is%20a%20very%20tricky%20demand%20because%20if%20they%E2%80%99re%20given%20some%20sort%20of%20separate%20administration%2C%20it%20will%20fracture%20Manipur%2C%20because%20the%20Nagas%20immediately%20would%20want%20to%20join%20up%20with%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20all%20that%20would%20be%20left%20is%20the%20Imphal%20valley.%20And%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20you%20can%20also%20understand%20that%20after%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20gone%20through%2C%20the%20Kuki%20clearly%20want%20some%20measure%20of%20autonomy%20to%20be%20able%20to%20safeguard%20themselves.%20So%20how%20would%20you%2C%20if%20you%20were%20home%20secretary%20now%2C%20tackle%20this%20extremely%20difficult%20situation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20of%20the%20view%20that%E2%80%A6%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20as%20joint%20secretary%20(northeast)%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20even%20a%20literally%2C%20an%20affidavit%20of%20mine%20in%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Manipur.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20said%20that%20even%20during%20the%20Naga%20talks%20and%20so%20on%20%E2%80%93%20we%20are%20not%20touching%20that.%20If%20you%20are%20not%20touching%20that%2C%20then%20the%20issue%20then%20becomes%20a%20matter%20of%20autonomy.%20You%20got%20the%20Hill%20Areas%20Council%2C%20which%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20worked%20because%20again%20the%20state%E2%80%A6%20no%20state%20government%20likes%20to%20give%20autonomy.%20It%E2%80%99s%20happened%20in%20Assam%20when%20you%20had%20Sixth%20Schedule%20status%20and%20even%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20areas.%20When%20we%20negotiated%20the%20Bodo%20Accord%2C%20we%20gave%20a%20lot%20of%20autonomy%20but%20they%20still%20feel%20that%20because%20the%20money%20is%20routed%20through%20the%20state%20government%2C%20who%20controls%20the%20money%2C%20controls%20everything%20else.%20So%20unless%20there%20is%20financial%20autonomy%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20difficult%20for%20anybody%20to%20feel%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20really%20autonomous.%E2%80%9D%20Therefore%2C%20an%20autonomous%20council%2C%20an%20autonomous%20area%20is%20fine.%20It%20can%20be%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule.%20I%20think%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20even%20in%20Manipur%20there%E2%80%99s%20been%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20apply%20to%20Manipur.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20it%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20can%20be%20applied.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20extended%20to%20any%20particular%20area%20which%20the%20government%20wants.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20Manipur%20governments%20have%20said%20that%20this%20is%20acceptable%20but%20this%20is%20something%20to%20be%20negotiated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20reports%20in%20the%20papers%20that%20the%20talks%20that%20were%20happening%20with%20the%20SoO%20%5BSuspension%20of%20Operations%5D%20groups%20and%20the%20home%20ministry%20%E2%80%93%20which%20then%20got%20overtaken%2C%20when%20May%203%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20were%20reaching%20a%20sort%20of%20conclusion.%20Reports%20suggest%20the%20SoO%20groups%20were%20willing%20to%20concede%20that%20autonomous%20hill%20area%20councils%20or%20autonomous%20territorial%20councils%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20%E2%80%93%20would%20be%20acceptable.%20Now%2C%20the%20Kuki%20say%20that%20the%20door%20is%20closed.%20Do%20you%20think%20it%20can%20be%20reopened%3F%20Can%20this%20package%20be%20sweetened%20to%20make%20the%20Kuki%20accept%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20can%20be%20reopened.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20question%20of%E2%80%A6%20you%20have%20to%20give%20it%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time.%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20allow%20the%20other%20processes%20which%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%E2%80%A6%20the%20step-by-step%20processes%20in%20terms%20of%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20leave%20this%20to%20the%20last.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20leave%20this%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20down%20the%20line.%20Because%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20anything%E2%80%A6%20forget%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20forget%20UT%2C%20forget%20a%20new%20state%2C%20etc.%2C%20will%20be%20discussed%20at%20all.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20too%20early.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20too%20early%2C%20so%20that%E2%80%99s%20two-three%20years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20as%20I%20put%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20you%E2%80%99re%20also%20suggesting%20that%20to%20make%20the%20hill%20area%20councils%20or%20the%20autonomous%20territorial%20districts%20or%20whatever%20you%20call%20them%20acceptable%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20have%20to%20also%20apply%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20closer%20to%20the%20Bodoland%20structure.%20And%20perhaps%2C%20in%20addition%2C%20give%20them%20also%20some%20measure%20of%20financial%20autonomy.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20that%20is%2C%20those%20are%20parts%20which%20can%20be%20negotiated%20with%20over%20a%20period%E2%80%A6%20I%20put%20it%20as%20I%20think%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20two%20three-years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20when%20all%20other%20things%E2%80%A6%20As%20I%20said%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20hoping%20that%20slowly%20all%20the%20other%20positive%20steps%20will%20take%20place%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%2C%20and%20this%20is%20my%20great%20fear%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20for%20two-three%20months%2C%20I%20think%20by%20November-December%2C%20I%20think%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20relative%20calm.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20lurking%20fear%20that%20you%20might%20again%20end%20up%20with%20another%20burst%20of%20violence.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20you%20say%20till%20November-December%E2%80%A6%20What%20worries%20you%20after%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20umber%20of%20issues.%20From%20one%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20looking%20at%20the%20whole%20issue%2C%20there%20are%20some%20issues%20which%20are%20taking%20place%E2%80%A6%20the%20poppy%20cultivation%20gets%20harvested%20in%20November%2C%20so%20nobody%20wants%E2%80%A6%20Both%20sides%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anything%20which%20might%20affect%20the%20cultivation%20of%20poppy.%20So%20many%20issues%20are%20there%20on%20the%20back%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20I%20understand%20correctly%2C%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20is%20that%20both%20sides%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20ensuring%20that%20the%20poppy%20harvest%20is%20not%20affected.%20Both%20sides%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20watching%20to%20see%20how%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20reacts%2C%20which%20is%20why%20there%20will%20be%20a%20sense%20of%20relative%20calm%20until%20November-December.%20Your%20worry%20is%20once%20the%20poppy%20harvest%20is%20done%20and%20once%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20perhaps%2C%20turned%20its%20attention%20to%20other%20matters%2C%20the%20situation%20can%20flare%20up%20again%2C%20around%20November-December.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20I%20mentioned%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20earlier%20steps%20like%20recovery%20of%20all%20looted%20arms%3B%20getting%20the%20administration%20in%20these%20areas%20back%3B%20%5Bearning%20the%5D%20trust%20of%20the%20people%3B%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20too%20many%20sporadic%20issues%20which%20keep%20tension%20rising%3B%20%C2%A0but%20there%20is%20a%20sort%20of%20gradual%20calming%E2%80%A6%20people%20feel%20things%20are%20back%20to%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThose%20are%20critical%20steps.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20critical%20steps%2C%20because%20otherwise%2C%20if%20you%20have%203%2C000-4%2C000%20arms%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20more%2C%20which%20come%20in%20from%20across%20the%20border%20and%20so%20on%20%E2%80%93%20you%20are%20sitting%20on%20a%20tinder%20box%20which%20you%20have%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20%E2%80%93%20can%20always%20blow%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20problem%20is%20those%20critical%20steps%20are%20not%20happening.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20discussed%20them%20in%20detail%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20happening.%20We%20have%20to%20keep%20our%20fingers%20crossed%20and%20hope%20and%20pray%20that%20they%20do%20happen.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20important%20that%20they%20happen%20if%20you%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20larger%2C%20long-term%20interests%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20last%20question.%20There%20is%20one%20ominous%20sign%20on%20the%20horizon%20and%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20you%20whether%20it%20worries%20you.%20Recent%20statements%20issued%20by%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%20increasingly%20suggest%20that%20the%20Nagas%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20talking%20about%20the%20Manipuri%20Nagas%2C%20the%20Tangkhul%20Nagas%20%E2%80%93%20are%20siding%20with%20the%20Meitei%20against%20the%20Kuki.%20A%20statement%20issued%20by%20Mr%20Th.%20Muivah%20%5Bwho%20is%20leading%20the%20Naga%20Peace%20Talks%5D%20from%20%5BCamp%5D%20Hebron%2C%20seems%20to%20suggest%20the%20same%20thing.%20Does%20this%20worry%20you%3F%20Is%20there%20here%20a%20potential%20for%20a%20second%20conflict%20happening%3F%20We%E2%80%99ve%20already%20got%20a%20Meitei-Kuki%20one%2C%20could%20there%20now%20be%20a%20Kuki-Naga%20one%20developing%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20so.%20I%20think%20the%20NSCN%20%5BI-M%5D%20and%20Muivah%2C%20what%20they%20are%20really%2C%20basically%20%5Bdoing%5D%20is%20stressing%20is%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20the%20Nagas.%20Which%20is%20why%20I%20said%2C%20any%20settlement%20you%20have%20with%20the%20Kukis%20etc%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20leave%20us%20out%20of%20it.%20Because%20there%20are%20Naga%20interests%20involved%2C%20both%20in%20the%20autonomy%20which%20can%20be%20given%20to%20the%20hill%20areas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20areas%20where%20supposedly%20Kuki%20dominance%20is%20there.%20But%20the%20Nagas%20may%20say%20that%20those%20are%20some%20areas%2C%20we%20also%20have%20influence%20in%20those%20areas%2C%20so%20don%E2%80%99t%20count%20us%20out%2C%20we%20want%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20those%20negotiations.%20Which%20is%20fair%E2%80%A6%20and%20I%20think%20the%20whole%20package%20of%20autonomy%20will%20come%20up%20with%20the%20Naga%20Peace%20Talks%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20autonomy%20for%20the%20Nagas%2C%20autonomy%20for%20the%20Kukis%2C%20and%20autonomy%20for%20the%20Zomis%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F19122134%2Fmuivah.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F19122134%2Fmuivah.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F19122134%2Fmuivah-300x148.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F19122134%2Fmuivah-1024x503.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-486611%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22590%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETh%20Muivah.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20Naga%20United%20Council%20is%20doing%2C%20is%20not%20spoiling%20for%20a%20fight%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20simply%20putting%20its%20card%20down%20on%20the%20table%2C%20and%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CListen%20folks!%20Don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20about%20us.%E2%80%9D%20Right%20in%20other%20words%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20making%20its%20presence%20felt%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20actually%20spoiling%20for%20a%20fight%2C%20even%20though%20they%E2%80%99ve%20accused%20the%20Kuki%20of%20false%20history%20and%20lies.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20just%20their%20way%20of%20saying%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20about%20us.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20so.%20And%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20they%20will%20spoil%20for%20a%20fight.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Naga%20should%20be%20most%20worried%20because%2C%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Imphal%2C%20they%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely.%3C%2Fstr