ensitive%20and%20delicate%20situation%20for%20years%20to%20come.%20We%20just%20have%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20about%20how%20we%20handle%20Manipur.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20we%20have%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20how%20we%20handle%20Manipur.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20not%20only%20must%20the%20government%20in%20Imphal%20keep%20its%20eyes%20open%20and%20its%20ears%20open%20and%20respond%20quickly%2C%20so%20must%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20for%20laxity%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20for%20people%20diverting%20their%20attention.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20we%20can%20afford%20it%20at%20all.%20I%20mean%20this%20is%20something%20which%20has%20both%2C%20not%20just%20domestic%20implications%2C%20it%20has%20international%20ramifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYes%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20interpreted%20as%20Hindu%20versus%20Christian%2C%20abroad.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20the%20violence%20of%20the%20civilwWar%20in%20Myanmar%20goes%20out%20of%20control%2C%20then%20you%20can%20expect%20refugees%20to%20come%20in%20bigger%20numbers%E2%80%A6%20like%20you%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20in%20Europe%20from%20Africa%2C%20you%20know.%20Every%20time%20you%20have%E2%80%A6%20in%20Sudan%20or%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20in%20all%20these%20countries%2C%20you%20have%20civil%20war%20and%20all%20of%20them%20finally%20take%20a%20boat%20and%20swim%20across.%20Here%2C%20this%20is%20just%20across.%20They%E2%80%99ll%20come%20here%20and%20those%20which%20are%20on%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20addition%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%20kinship%20because%20the%20same%20tribes%20are%20split%20between%20Myanmar%20and%20India%2C%20and%20sometimes%20India-Bangladesh%20as%20well.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20thank%20you%20for%20opening%20our%20eyes%2C%20I%20thank%20you%20for%20the%20honesty%20with%20which%20yo