t%3A%20Yati%20Gaur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20he%20faces%20while%20on%20his%20walking%20expeditions%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20in%20India%20have%20largely%20been%20wonderful%20and%20helpful%20to%20me.%20The%20only%20issue%20that%20I%20face%20sometimes%20is%20finding%20pet-friendly%20hotels%20to%20stay%20in.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20the%20hotels%20I%20book%20say%20that%20they%20are%20pet-friendly%20but%20end%20up%20asking%20me%20to%20keep%20Buttercup%20outside%20the%20room.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20little%20difficult%20to%20find%20another%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20technology%20is%20his%20other%20companion%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20Google%20Maps%20does%20not%20work%20or%20show%20the%20wrong%20distance.%20Even%20if%20the%20map%20shows%20fewer%20kilometres%2C%20it%20can%20become%20at%20least%20a%20half%20hour%20more%20of%20walking.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20try%20to%20travel%20as%20light%20as%20I%20can%20with%20minimal%20clothing%20and%20essentials%20like%20medicines%20and%20toiletries.%20I%20also%20try%20to%20avoid%20using%20gadgets%20while%20walking%20to%20save%20as%20much%20battery%20as%20I%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwSVkTPhq60%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwSVkTPhq60%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20