0Delhi-based%20non-profit%20India%20HIV%2FAIDS%20Alliance%20with%20PLHIV%20in%20the%20sex%20worker%20and%20transgender%20community%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20who%20struggle%20with%20drug%20addiction.%20Under%20the%20programme%2C%20he%20helps%20them%20overcome%20stigma%20and%20misinformation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20assists%20them%20in%20accessing%20counselling%2C%20getting%20a%20timely%20diagnosis%2C%20and%20referring%20them%20to%20government%20hospitals%20for%20treatment.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20helped%20more%20than%20500%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277257%2Fchennai-man-adopts-children-living-with-hiv-shelter-trust-solomon-raj%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20living%20with%20HIV%20%3C%2Fa%3Eget%20over%20the%20stigma%20and%20get%20the%20correct%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Gautam%20to%20understand%20what%20it%20has%20been%20like%20for%20him%20to%20live%20with%20HIV%20for%20so%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98People%20say%20I%20should%20die%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20teenager%2C%20Gautam%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20much%20about%20different%20sexual%20orientations.%20A%20conversation%20with%20Prince%20Manvendra%20Singh%20Gohil%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20openly%20gay%20prince%20%E2%80%94%20was%20his%20introduction%20to%20his%20own%20sexuality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLike%20any%20other%20teenager%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20and%20why%20it%20was%20happening%20to%20me.%20I%20felt%20alone.%20Back%20in%202008%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20sufficient%20access%20to%20the%20internet.%20Through%20interviews%20on%20television%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20homosexuality.%20I%20contacted%20Prince%20Manvendra%2C%20who%20advised%20me%20to%20connect%20with%20Naz%20Foundation.%20Through%20counselling%2C%20I%20understood%20I%20am%20gay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%