ain%20them.%20Next%2C%20we%20customise%20a%20unit%20design%20for%20them%2C%20and%20when%20they%20implement%20it%2C%20we%20keep%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20their%20work%20every%20day%20through%20video%20calls%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Pinak%20Suryavanshi%20(24)%20who%20hails%20from%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sangli%20district%2C%20switched%20to%20hydroponics%20farming%20last%20year%20with%20Ashwin%E2%80%99s%20assistance.%20%E2%80%9CI%20live%20in%20a%20region%20where%20we%20face%20intense%20water%20scarcity.%20In%20a%20situation%20like%20this%2C%20we%20had%20to%20waste%20an%20uncalculated%20amount%20of%20water%20to%20grow%20green%20fodder%20on%20a%20large%20land.%20But%20with%20hydroponics%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20get%20500%20kilos%20of%20fodder%20daily%20by%20using%20500%20litres%20of%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-1692278302.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashwin%20has%20trained%20more%20than%208%2C000%20farmers%20and%20entrepreneurs%20to%20adopt%20hydroponic%20farming%20techniques.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-1692278302.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-1692278302-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-1692278302-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-1692278302-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-1692278302-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327482%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%